(913, 5, 'Amrita Inn', 'No 18,Jawaharlal Nehru Salai,Arumbakkam,Chennai Arumbakkam', 'A good accommodation option for business travellers, Amrita Inn is in proximity to commercial and shopping hubs of Chennai. You can easily reach the hotel from Chennai Central railway station (8.1 km) and Chennai International Airport (12 km). Â  The hotel features an air-conditioned, multi-purpose hall for hosting business meets and private gatherings. 24-hour room service, cab facility, laundry service, travel desk, parking, currency exchange, luggage storage, high-speed internet connectivity and power backup are also offered here. Â  You can book one of the 37 AC/non-AC rooms that come equipped with LCD TV, wardrobe, writing desk, STD/ISD direct-dial telephone and 24-hour hot/cold water supply. Â  Fish and Prawn, the hotels multi-cuisine restaurant serves Continental, and Chettinad cuisine. Â  T Nagar, one of the busiest shopping districts in Chennai, is 4.8 km from the hotel. You can offer prayers at Vadapalani Murugan Temple (1.6 km) or spend quality time at Marina Beach (10.5 km).', 7480, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(914, 29, 'Hotel Siddhivinayak Inn WALUJ', 'Hotel Siddhivinayak Inn, RM-2,Maharana Pratap Chowk,Waluj,Aurangabad', 'Hotel Siddhivinayak Inn WALUJ is situated in Aurangabad. Famous attraction near by this property is Siddharth Garden (10 km), Panchakki (11 km), Bibi Ka Maqbara (12 km), Jain Temple (13 km), Aurangabad Caves (14 km) and many more. Nearest means of transportation from this property is Aurangabad Airport (19 km), Aurangabad Railway Station (11 km) and Aurangabad Central Bus Station (10 km). This property host facilities like 24 hour room service, credit card acceptance, parking, 24 hour power backup, laundry services, travel desk and many more. In emergency this property offer doctor on call facility to its guest. The hotel houses a restaurant, serving flavoursome delicacies that will surely pamper your appetite. One can also opt for state transport or can hire a private vehicle to reach the property. This hotel offer well furnished room with modern amenities. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Hotel Siddhivinayak Inn WALUJ!', 9148, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(915, 423, 'Sri Krishna Guest House', '29/31,Ranagapillai Street Pondicherry', 'Sri Krishnas Guest House, roughly a 5 minute drive from Puducherry Railway Station, is located on Ayyanar Koil Street. The Basilica of the Sacred Heart of Jesus is barely a 5-minute drive from here. Guests can choose their accommodation from well-maintained rooms, which are provided with amenities like cable TV, direct dial telephone and air conditioner. All rooms have attached bathrooms that are provided with necessary toiletries. The travel desk makes requisite arrangements for guests to explore nearby attractions of the region. Other conveniences provided here include laundry, airport transfer and taxi service. With the help of diligent staff, the property ensures that guests have a hassle-free stay. Plenty of dining and wining options are available close to the guest house, where guests can relish local as well as international delicacies. Those who wish to dine without leaving the comfort of their rooms can avail the facility of room service. Guests can enjoy an evening stroll and savour lip-smacking dishes in different restaurants at Seaside Promenade that is only a 10 minute drive from the property.', 7457, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(916, 411, 'Golden Sands Betalbatim', 'Golden Sand, Ranwado, Betalbatim Salcete', 'Nestled in Goa, the city known for its natural picturesque beauty, attractive beaches, famous architectural temples and grand parties is flocked by the tourists from all over the world. Golden Sands Betalbatim is a delightful leisure with an absolute blend of service, charm and efficiency. It offers doctor on call, laundry, front desk, room service and many more. Food lovers can relish authentic and multi-cuisine dishes at the in-house swanky restaurant. Stocking a collection of choicest beverages, the on-site bar is an ideal place to relax and unwind after a hectic day out. The guest rooms have graceful interior design infused with a warm ambiance. They are enlightened with comfort which makes visitors stay memorable. They are equipped with air-conditioners, television, tea/coffee maker, clean linen and many other requisite amenities. All the rooms have neat attached bathrooms with essential toiletries. Nearest means of transportation from this property is Mapusa Bus station, Thivim Railway station and Goa International Airport. One can also opt for state transport or can hire a private vehicle to reach the property. Cool off and have a relax stay at Golden Sands Betalbatim!', 6588, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0);
