(917, 422, 'Jayam Castle', '198 Hollywood Hills Pudhu Nagar,', 'Jayam Castle is an independent bungalow nestled in one of the most famous hill station in India, Ooty. Dotted with lush green lawn and trees all around, the property look beautiful. It is located at the distance of 2.8 km from Ooty Railway Station and Mani Vihar Bus Stand. The nearest airport is Coimbatore airport. Guests can also take taxi services and cabs from Bangalore and Mysore. A well-furnished property is an ideal place for those who want to burst stress from city life. It provides well maintained bed rooms, balcony sit outs, living room and Dinning room. Moreover property also features fully equipped kitchenette. Its easy accessibility to prominent landmarks of the town, simple accommodations and provision of necessary amenities like housekeeping, parking, travel assistance, pick and drop from airport and doctor on call service in case of medical emergencies to ensure a relaxed and comfortable stay. While their stay guests can visit many famous tourist places in and around like Government Museum(1.1 km), Ooty Lake(2.2 km), Kandal Cross Shrine(1.1 km), Government Botanical Garden(3.8 km), Doddabetta Peak(10.2 km) and many others are situated at a feasible distance from the bungalow. Have a delightful experience at the well-menicured lush green surroundings!', 3020, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(918, 269, 'Hotel Kasturi Palace', '51A, Hill Cart Road, Rose Bank Rose Bank', 'Hotel Kasturi Palace is a 2 star property nestled in the tranquillity and beautiful scenery of Darjeeling. The hotel is located 1 km from Darjeeling Railway Station and at walking distance from the bus stop. Famous sightseeing places situated in nearby area of the property are Batasia Loop (2.7 km), Bhutia Busty Monastery (3.1 km), Peace Pagoda (3.4 km), Padmaja Naidu Himalayan Zoological Park (4.3 km) and Tiger Hill (9.7 km). Bagdogra Airport is located at distance of 68.5 km. Rooms of the hotel are aesthetically designed and equipped with modern amenities like television, intercom, newspaper, geyser, hot/cold running water and essential bathroom toiletries. A spacious and well-appointed accommodation offers services like parking, laundry, airport/railway station transfers and room service. In medical emergencies, guests can avail doctor on call service. Foodies are in for a gastronomic treat at the on-site restaurant, which severs mouth-watering regional and Indian delicacies. Have a funfull stay at the Hotel Kasturi Palace!', 7171, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(919, 269, 'Hotel Mount View', 'Gandhi Road, Near Circuit House Gandhi Road', 'Hotel Mount View at Darjeeling is a budget property, located barely at 100 metres from Railway Station, 500 metres from the NBSTC Bus Station and 14 km from Bagdogra Airport, The hotel is in close proximity to Hong Kong Market (2 km), Savin Kingdom 2.3 km, Iskon Temple (5.2 km), Salugara Monastery (6.4 km), and many more. The hotel features comfortable and well-appointed rooms equipped with basic amenities which include LCD television, telephone facility, 24 hours running Hot/Cold water, laundry service, transportation facility for tour and travel. Guests can enjoy the regional and local delicacies around the property. Have a Great stay at Hotel Mount View!', 9571, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(920, 4, 'The Signature Inn', '#479, OTC Road, CottonPet, Bangalore Cottonpet', 'A budget hotel, 5 kms from MG Road, 1.2 kms from Chickpete Located in the commercial hub of Bangalore, The Signature Inn features luxurious and well-furnished rooms. All the rooms are equipped with air-conditioners, cable televisions, intercom, tea/coffee makers and bathroom toiletries. Commercial centers such as Avenue Road, City Market, B.V.K Iyengar Road etc are at a walking distance from the hotel. For the convenience and comfortable stay of guests, the hotel offers internet facility, room service, laundry, doctor on call, taxi services, sightseeing and parking space in basement. Bangalore International Exhibition Centre is 19 kilometres while the shopping destinations such as MG Road, Brigade Road, Commercial Street, Mantri Mall ,UB City and Orion Mall are 3-5 kilometres from the hotel, which makes the hotel convenient to both leisure and business travellers. In-house restaurant services wide array of North and South Indian cuisines. Also, room service is available at the hotel. 500 mts from Railway Station and Majestic Bus StandEasy accessibility to the main market areas and economical rates make the hotel a ideal spot for accommodation in Bangalore.', 9592, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(921, 59, 'The Presidency Classic', '1471/a  nayapalli 1471/a  nayapalli', 'Around 6 km from Biju Patnaik International Airport, The Presidency Classic is a good choice for leisure travellers. Ekamra Kanan Botanical Gardens and Regional MuseumÃ‚Â of NaturalÃ‚Â History are within 3 km from the hotel. Ã‚Â  It offers a salon, gymnasium and full-service spa for the fitness and wellness needs of guests. Banquet halls, sightseeing tours, free parking, laundry service and doctor on call are also available. Ã‚Â  The hotels 48 spacious and well-furnished rooms feature satellite television, telephone, Wi-Fi and electric kettle. En suite bathrooms have 24-hour cold/hot water supply. Ã‚Â  Guests can choose from a wide variety of dishes served at the hotels multi-cuisine restaurant. Ã‚Â  While staying here, visit ISKCONÃ‚Â Temple (350 m) and Museum of Tribal Arts and Artifacts (1.8 km). The famous Nandankanan Zoological Park is a short 20-minute drive away.', 4758, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(922, 409, 'River Tern Homestay', 'River Tern Homestay, Nakoor Village  Kanbail Post, Sunticoppa-571237 Raichur', 'River Tern Homestay is a budget property located in the beautiful Coorg. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks help. The hotel offers recreational facilities like country boat-ride, coracle ride, campfire, trekking, fishing, boating, swimming and tree house. Guests can choose to stay in spacious and well-maintained rooms that are provided with all essential conveniences to make the stay pleasurable for guests. The rooms feature simple decor, furnishings and amenities like bedroom and bathrooms with essential bathroom toiletries. The doctor on call facility can be availed during medical emergencies. A cook is available round the clock to cook various regional and local delicacies as per the needs of the guests. The nearest airport and railway station are Mysore Airport and Mysore Junction respectively. Have a pleasant stay at River Tern Homestay!', 7617, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(923, 410, 'Hotel Kumar Residency', 'Town Bhagsunag, Post Office Mcleodganj, District Kangdra Bhagsunag, Meleodganj', 'Hotel Kumar Residency is located in Dharamshala and is 18.9 km from Gaggal Airport Dharamshala, 38.2 km from Kangra Mandir Railway Station and 25.6 km from Shahpur Bus Stand. Dharamshala is surrounded by dense coniferous forest consisting mainly of stately Deodar cedar trees and is in the upper reaches of the Kangra Valley. Tourist attraction to visit in Dharamshala are Tibetan Institute of Performing Arts(2.4 km), Dal Lake-Mcleod Ganj(2.7 km), St. John in the Wilderness(2.8 km), Tushita Meditation Centre(2.8 km), H H Dalai Lama Main Temple(2.9 km), Bhagsu Falls(7.1 km) and Church Of St. John in the Wilderness(7.1 km). The hotel features facilities such as travel assistance, taxi, bus/train booking and room service. Trekking and adventure activities are available on request. Rooms of the property are spacious, luxurious and clean. In-room amenities are LCD television and balcony. Attached bathroom have supply of hot/cold water and essential toiletries. Restaurant serve tasty and finger licking food dishes. Have a pleasant stay at Hotel Kumar Residency!', 8294, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(924, 207, 'Lake Palace Luxury Backwater Resort', 'Alleppey Alleppey', 'The property is nestled in which is simply the most magical place on the earth. During the monsoon season, tourists can witness the true splendours of Alleppey. Lake Palace Luxury Backwater Resort offers luxurious service apartments that are specifically designed to make the stay comfortable. The hotel is located at an accessible distance from Cochin International Airport and Alleppey Railway Station (5.7 km).   To ease the stress of travel, the property offers conveniences such as Wi-Fi, valet parking, wakeup call service, laundry, front desk and mmany more for the pleasurable stay of guests. Holidaymakers can avail the service of travel desk in planning a suitable itinerary as per their budget and needs. In case of medical emergency doctor on call facility is also provided by the hotel. There is a coffee shop where they can enjoy light snacks with refreshing beverages.   The multi-cuisine restaurant of the hotel has a perfect setting where guests can enjoy scrumptious regional, Chinese and Continental dishes. For business travellers who want to host meetings and conferences, the resort has a stylish and well-appointed conference hall. Guests can avail rejuvenating massage therapies and treatments at the in-house spa. While staying here, guests can enjoy a refreshing dip in the swimming pool or simply relax beside it. Fitness lovers can start their day at in-house fitness center and enjoy their workout.   The rooms are well furnished with unique interiors with a feel of an upscale home including comfy beds and comfortable linens. Evoking the grandeur and opulence, all rooms are finely appointed with all necessary room amenities like television and many more. The professional and attentive staff of the hotel is always ready to help guests to make their stay a delightful one. All rooms have attached bathrooms well equipped with essential bathroom amenities and toiletries along with hot/cold water supply.   The property has an advantage as it enjoys propinquity to various places like Alleppey Beach (5.8 km), The Sri Krishna Temple (17 km), Pathiramanal (18.5 km), Karumadi (19.3 km) and many more.Shoppers may indulge in shopping spree at various shopping places located close to the property.   Experience a great stay and a warm hospitality at Lake Palace Luxury Backwater Resort!', 8320, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(925, 410, 'Hotel Upper City Heart', 'Naddi Naddi', 'Tucked away from city center, Hotel Upper City Heart is beautifully located in the close proximity to Airport, Railway station and bus stand. The hotel is in amidst nature and surrounded by dense coniferous forest. Some of the prominent famous tourist excursions are Kangra Valley, Bhagsu Falls, St. John in the Wilderness, Kareri Lake, Chintpurni and various other notable spots are in the close vicinity to the property. The rooms in the hotel are well-maintained, ventilated, clean, also comes with good quality furniture to provide comfort and revival feeling equipped with modern conveniences like cable television, intercom, telephone, tea/coffee maker, room heater, attached bathroom and various other substantive bathroom toiletries. For a relaxed and easy stay in this tranquil and lush landscape, an array of facilities such as internet connectivity, laundry, room service and parking space. Services such as taxi service, airport/railway transfers, guide service, sightseeing, executive lounge and yoga classes are available at an extra cost. The multi-cuisine restaurant of the hotel has a perfect setting where guests can enjoy scrumptious regional, Mughlai, Gujarati, Bengali, Punjabi, Chinese and Tandoori dishes to whirl up your taste-buds. The decent ornate, pleasant ambiance at Hotel Upper City Heart makes you feel all comfortable in no time!', 5315, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(926, 410, 'Hotel Amandeep', 'Mcloadganj Road, District Kangra Mcloadganj Road, District Kangra', 'Hotel Amandeep is located in Dharamshala. The nearest airport is at Gaggal which is well connected to major cities. And the closest railway station is in Pathankot making it convenient for the guest to reach. Hotel facilitates laundry services, airport and railway station transfer, taxi services and doctor on call is available in any medical emergency. The property has well equipped rooms with amenities like television, sofa unit and intercom facility. Each room has attached washroom with regular supply of hot and cold water. Room service is available for the convenience of guest. Popular tourist attractions in Dharamshala are Dharmasthala Temple, Lord Manjunatha, Bahubali, Manjusha Museum, Netravathi River Barrage, Ram Mandir, Badinede Betta, Shri Chandranatha Swamy Basadi and many more. Have a comfortable and pleasant stay at Amandeep!', 7872, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(927, 269, 'Hotel Broadway', '4, Cooch Behar Road Cooch Behar Road', 'Less than 1 km from Darjeeling railway station and Dhirdham Temple, Hotel Broadway is popular with leisure travelers. The hotel offers airport/railway station transfers, banquet/conference facilities, travel desk, WiFi, doctor on call and car parking. It also arranges sightseeing and trekking tours on request.   Featuring wooden decor, the hotels Double and Family rooms come with satellite TV, telephone and hot/cold water supply. A common balcony on every floor offers panoramic mountain views. Savour Chinese and Indian dishes at the in-house restaurant.   Himalayan Tibet Museum and Mahakal Temple are less than 10 minutes walk from the hotel. Enjoy local food or buy souvenirs from curio shops at Chowk Bazaar (1.2 km).', 9059, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(928, 84, 'The Citi Pride', 'opp jhulelal temple diggi chowk, ajmer', 'Wrapped in the barren hills of the Aravallis and holding a blue lake in the heart, Ajmer, The Citi Pride is a boutique property, where luxury manifests itself. It is a one-stop destination for quality accommodations at affordable prices. This value for money property offers immense delight to its guests by offering superior accommodation with heaven of comfort and hospitality. The nearest airport and railway station to the region is Jaipur Airport and Ajmer Junction Railway Station. The property offers quite elegant and magnificent accommodation that offers conveniences like front desk and many more. The rooms of the hotel are a blend of beauty and comfort with stylish interiors and spacious to move around freely. Quite capacious and elegant rooms are complete with essential room amenities that fortifies delightful stay for guests. They have neat and clean attached bathrooms equipped with necessary toiletries. Have a relaxed and memorable stay at The Citi Pride!', 5919, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(929, 84, 'Hotel Mansingh Palace', 'Vaishali Nagar Vaishali Nagar', 'Hotel Mansingh Palace is a budget property located in the heart of Rajasthan, Ajmer, bustling chaotic city surrounded by Aravalli mountain range. The hotel is located at a distance of 29.8 km from Kishangarh Airport, 3.6 km from Ajmer Railway Station, 2.8 km from Ajmer Bus Stand. The hotel has nearby tourist attractions like Adhai Din Ka Jhopra(3.8 km), Anasagar Lake(4.1 km), Ajmer Sharif(4.2 km), Taragarh Fort(6 km), Pushkar(12.7 km) and many more. Those with religious interests can also visit famous Brahma Temple(13 km). The hotel offers facilities such as front desk, laundry, dry cleaning, bell stand, currency exchange, fax, safe vault. For immediate care of guests doctor on call facility is also available. Guests can savor lip smacking delectable dishes in restaurant and can also relish evening drinks at bar. The rooms of the hotel are centrally air conditioned, well equipped with room amenities like air conditioning, electronic safe deposit, LED television, hair dryer, tea/coffee maker, mini fridge. The rooms are also well equipped with all basic bathroom amenities and toiletries. Have a pleasant stay at Hotel Mansingh Palace!', 6968, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
