(932, 240, 'Grand Pacific Retreat', '39km Ambala Chandigarh Highway, Near Omaxe Appartment Village Jharmari, Distt Mohali', 'Located in the modern city, Ambala. Grand Pacific Retreat Hotel is located at a distance of 32.2km from Chandigarh Airport, 14.4 km from Ambala Cantt Junction and 10.4 km from city bus stand. Perfectly blends the tradition of hospitality with modern day facilities like room service, free WiFi, doctor on call, fax copier, computer service and in house laundry service. Guest can also avail some other services on request like car rental, travel assistance, indoor/ outdoor banquet facilities, Wedding and other event planning. Well-maintained and spacious rooms available at the property and amenities like internet connection, satellite television, telephone, tea/coffee maker, mini bar on request, hair dryer on request, safe deposit locker on request and attached bathroom with hot/cold water and essential bathroom toiletries. Relish authentic and flavorful dishes in the serene ambiance of the in-house swanky restaurant offering a memorable dining experience. Flavorsome beverages and lip-smacking snacks can be relished at the Coffee Shop. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Grand Pacific Retreat!', 7564, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
