(1201, 16, 'Monarch Hotel', 'Sector-3, Sagar Kuti Chaurah, Opp. AVTEC Ltd. Pithampur , Opp. AVTEC Ltd. Pithampur', '|Barely a 40-minute drive from Indore Junction Railway Station, Monarch Hotel is situated close to the Kalibillod area of the city. There is a conference hall at the premises that allows guests to arrange and attend official as well as social events. The travel desk helps guests in planning sightseeing tours and visiting nearby attractions. Other conveniences include doctor-on-call, airport transfer, laundry and car parking.| To provide a comfortable stay to discerning travellers, the hotel offers well-maintained rooms, which are equipped with amenities like cable TV, direct dial telephone, study table and wardrobe. En suite bathrooms have shower area, essential toiletries and hot/cold water supply.| A wide array of culinary delights can be relished at the in-house restaurant, which offers lip-smacking dishes of different cuisine. For relishing exotic cocktails/mocktails, and scrumptious snacks, visit the on-site bar.| Annapurna Temple, roughly a 10-minute drive from here, is a must-visit religious centre for devotees to seek blessings.| |less', 6597, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1202, 16, 'Hotel Silver Shed', 'Plot No - 15, PU4, Scheme 54, Vijaynagar , Vijaynagar', '| Located 3.5 kilometers from Choki Dhani, Hotel Silver Shed features comfortable and well-appointed rooms equipped with modern conveniences. In-room amenities include cable television, intercom facility, mineral water, daily newspaper, iron/ironing board(on request) and Wi-Fi internet. | The hotel is in close proximity to Rajwada (6.5 km), Nehru Park, Kaanch Mandir (8.5 km), Lal Bagh Palace (9.5 km), Indore Airport (11.5 km) and offers transfer facilities.| The hotel houses a restaurant, serves delicious food that will perfectly suit your palate. | Chill out and have a lovely stay at Silver Shed! | |less', 6507, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1203, 17, 'Banyan Paradise Resort', 'Sama Savli Road, Nr Dumad Crossing, NH-8, Opposite to Hotel Plazzo Dumad', 'Conveniently located near Vadodara Airport (5 km), the boutique hotel offers comfortable stays for leisure and business travellers. Vadodara Bus Station and Vadodara Junction are about 8 km away.   Besides recreational facilities like outdoor swimming pool and indoor games, the hotel offers 3 banquet halls, 24-hour front desk, doctor on call, Wi-Fi (surcharge), parking space, car rental and lawn for outdoor functions.   You can choose from 20 well-appointed rooms and suites with modern conveniences such as air conditioning, LCD TV, telephone, 24-hour room service, tea/coffee maker and Wi-Fi.   The hotels 24-hour multi-cuisine restaurant offers regional and international delicacies, and delicious desserts. It also has a coffee shop and bakery.   Tourist attractions like Laxmi Vilas Palace, Sayaji Baug and Baroda Museum and Picture gallery are within 10 km from the property. Guests can also head to The Inorbit Mall (8.6 km) that houses a wellness centre, international brands and food courts.', 4879, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1204, 17, 'Hotel Casa', 'Above Saraswat Co. Op. Bank, Opp. Rangoli Restaurant, Fatehgunj Main Road Fatehgunj Camp road', 'Situated in the happening city of Vadodra, Hotel Casa is a modern charismatic property located at a distance of 3.5 km from Vadodara Airport while Vadodara Junction is 1.6 km and Central Bus Stand Road is 1.4 km away. Guest can vist famous tourist attraction like Baroda Museum and Picture Gallery(1 km), Sayaji Baug(1.2 km), EME Temple(2 km), Laxmi Villas Palace(3.2 km), Nazar Baug Palace(4.7 km) and many more. Amidst the most beautiful architecture and luxurious interiors, the hotel features various modern facilities like laundry service, Wi-Fi access, currency exchange, room service, front desk and parking. Beautifully decorated rooms here are fitted with modern conveniences such as air conditioner, television, mini bar, tea/coffee maker and attached bathrooms. The hotel offers a myriad of conveniences to make the stay comfortable for guests. Hotel Casa is all about the Luxury stay accomodation that comes at a Pocket friendly Price!', 8175, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0);
