(1205, 17, 'Four Points by Sheraton Vadodara', '1275, Ward No 7,Fatehgunj Fatehgunj Camp road', 'Four Points by Sheraton is situated in a graceful city of palaces, parks, temples and museums, Vadodara. It is located at a distance of 4 km from Vadodara Airport, 2 km from Vadodara Railway Station and 2 km from Vadodara Bus Station which makes it easy for the guest to commute. The property has fully furnished and equipped rooms with amenities like air conditioner, telephone, housekeeping services, mini bar and tea/coffee maker. Hotel facilitates luggage storage, laundry services, 24 hour security, concierge services, internet access, secretarial service, currency exchange, fitness center, car rental services and ballroom for wedding ceremony, birthday party and social gathering. The hotel has restaurant which serves mouthwatering and delicious dishes. Popular tourist attractions in Vadodara are Seven Seas Mall (350 m), EME Temple (2 km), Sayaji Baug (2 km), Baroda Museum (2 km), Inorbit Mall (3 km), Sursagar Lake (4 km), Kirti Stambh (4 km), Laxmi Vilas Palace (5 km), Iskcon Temple (5 km), Tapovan Temple (7 km) and many more. Have a memorable and comfortable stay at Four Points by Sheraton!', 4153, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1206, 17, 'Revival Lords Inn', 'University Road, Sayajigunj Sayajigunj', '1.3 km from Inorbit Mall, 1.7 km from Vadodara Railway Station, 2.8 km from Nehru Park, 4 Banquet halls, 2 On-site restaurants Revival Lords Inn is a strategically located property in Vadodara. This 3 star hotel is located about 5.5 km from Vasna Village Lake. The hotel provides a good selection of living options that are available in two choices- Deluxe and Executive Deluxe Rooms. All rooms are well-maintained and are equipped with amenities like cable TV, direct-dial phone, mini bar, tea/coffee maker and internet connectivity. The hotel houses four banquet halls of varying sizes within the premises. These halls are well-equipped and are ideal for hosting parties, functions, conferences and meetings. Other facilities like laundry, car parking and doctor-on-call are also offered at the hotel. Blue Coriander and Kala Patther are the two on-site restaurants that dish out a variety of international and South Indian dishes. Appealing decor and live gazals add charms to the fine dining experience. Choose garden view rooms to enjoy scenic beauty!', 3128, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1207, 17, 'The Taj Gateway Hotel, Akota', 'Akota Gardens Akota Gardens', '2.7 km from Vadodara Railway Station, 5.4 km from Lakshmi Narayan Nagar Lake, 8.0 km from Vadodara Airport, 2 Multi-cuisine restaurants, 3 Banquets halls, Business centre, Fitness centre, Swimming pool, Massage centre The Taj Gateway Hotel Akota Garden is a 5 star hotel, situated in the heart of the city centre. Popular attractions like Laxmi Vilas Palace, Sayaji Garden and Sursagar Lake lie in proximity to this hotel. The hotel has 89 rooms that are categorised as Standard Rooms, Superior Rooms, Executive Rooms and Suites. All rooms are equipped with premium amenities such as television with satellite channels, direct-dial telephone, safe deposit locker and tea/coffee maker. A fully equipped fitness centre, swimming pool, steam room and massage centre, allows guests enjoy their stay. A well-equipped business centre, three banquet halls and two meeting rooms offer ideal venues to host business meetings, events or wedding parties. The hotel provides free Wi-Fi upto 2 devices. In addition, the spacious lawns of the hotel are perfect for accommodating large gathering of up to 2500 people. Currency exchange, travel assistance and laundry are the services provided by the hotel. G A D-Gateway All Day -the in-house restaurant is the perfect venue to relish Indian and international cuisine. For Thai, Japanese and Chinese delicacies, guests can visit Kai Asia . Experience rejuvenating body massages at the massage centre or relax in the steam room.', 9546, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1208, 17, 'Hotel Mini Palace', 'Near Rosary School, Pratapgunj', 'Nestled in Vadodara, Hotel Mini Palace is at a distance of 4.5 km from Vadodara Airport, 800 m from Vadodara Railway Station and 4.9 km from Bus Stop. Various tourist places where guest can visit like Baroda Museum & Picture Gallery(1.5 km), Sayaji Baug(1.8 km), EME Temple(2.9 km), Laxmi Vilas Palace(3.9 km), Nazarbaug Palace(5.3 km) and much more. The rooms of the hotel are spacious airy and well maintained which makes staying here an absolute joy. The hotel also offers room service which ensures that the guests are well attended and their demands are met promptly. Have a pleasant stay at Hotel Mini Palace!', 4289, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1209, 17, 'Express Towers', 'R.C. Dutt Road , Alkapuri R.C. Dutt Road , Alkapuri', 'Located on R.C. Dutt Road, Express Towers is one of the prominent hotels in Vadodara. This 4 star hotel features 65 rooms that feature stylish and elegant interiors complete with modern furnishings. Guests can choose to stay in Executive Deluxe, Studio Suite or Suite category of rooms. Conveniences like LCD TV, ISDN telephone, electronic safe, Wi-Fi and mini bar are provided in all the rooms. With a business centre and three conference halls viz. Oaks Room, Cedar Room and Board Room, the hotel caters well to the needs of corporate. Moreover, the hotel also facilitates weddings and other social events. Facilities like Wi-Fi, airport pick-up, currency exchange, travel desk and laundry are also available at the hotel. Guests can relish authentic Gujarati dishes in a casual and modern setting at the in-house restaurant Mandap. Additionally, they can savour Thai and Chinese delights at the restaurant 24 Carats and freshly made cakes at the cake shop - Muffins. Gain an insight into city\'s heritage at Laxmi Vilas Palace or enjoy a boat ride on Sursagar Lake, which are located within 5 km radius of the hotel.', 6432, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
