(1217, 17, 'Hotel Kalyan FatehGunj', 'Fatehgunj Main Road Fatehgunj Main Road', 'About 5 km from Vadodara Airport, Hotel Kalyan is apt for leisure as well as transit travellers. Vadodara Junction is 1.5 km away. A team of friendly staff at the front desk assist guests in every possible way. Other conveniences include concierge service, laundry service, tour assistance and parking facility. Featuring floor-to-ceiling curtains, the 15 air-conditioned rooms come with comfortable bedding. LCD TV, Wi-Fi, wardrobe, kettle, work desk and sofa chairs are available in every room. You can relish North Indian, Gujarati and international dishes at the hotel’s multi-cuisine Kalyan Café. In-room dining service is also available. Exhibiting a fine collection of artworks and sculptures, Baroda Museum is merely 1 km away. The beautiful Sayaji Baug (2.1 km) and EME Temple (3 km) are other prominent attractions in Baroda.', 6381, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1218, 17, 'Vrundavan Residency', 'Near Siddhi Vinayak Temple Dandia Bazar Main Road', 'Hotel Vrundavan Residency is one of the finest budget hotels present in colorful city of Vadodra. Property can be reached via Vadodara Airport(5 km), Vadodara Railway Station(3.8 km) and 8 km from Main Bus Stand. Large, spacious rooms and suites of hotel are elegantly embellished with modernistic furniture, gorgeous interiors, complemented excellently with satellite TV, AC, telephone and refrigerators. The dimly lit 24 hours Room Service offers the blend of mouthwatering dishes & cuisine across the room. The hotel consists of 2 luxurious dormitories with 9 beds and 6 fresh rooms in it. These dormitories are beneficial for group bookings and marriages. The Hotel has designed these dormitories in such a way that you feel same freshness of separate rooms. Moreover one can also avail banquet hall for organising auspicious functions. While staying at this city, one must visit Laxmi Vilas Palace, Sayaji Baug, EME Temple, Baroda Museum, Nazarbaug Palace and much more.', 4549, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1219, 17, 'Aum Health Resort', 'Behind Rasulabad Gam, Ajwa Road, Jafarpura, Waghod Jafarpura, Waghodia, Vadodara', '', 6340, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1220, 17, 'Lemon Tree Hotel', 'Opp-Parsi Agyari, Sayajigunj Sayajigunj', 'Lemon Tree Hotel is a 4 star property located in the beautiful city of Vadodara. The hotel is situated at the distance of 5.1 km from Vadodara Airport, 550 mtrs from Vadodara Railway Station and 700 mtrs from Vadodara Bus Station. All rooms of the property are equipped with amenities like Wi-Fi, mini bar, tea/coffee maker and an electronic safe makes your stay cozy and comfortable. Guests can visit famous sightseeing places located near to the property such as Sayaji Baug (300 mtrs), Baroda Museum & Picture Gallery (2 km), Laxmi Vilas Palace (2.4 km), Kirti Stambh (2.5 km) and EME Temple (3.6 km). Hotel offers services like transportation, business desk and room service. Guests can enjoy mouthwatering and delicious food at in-house restaurant. Have a relaxing stay at Lemon Tree!', 9823, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1221, 17, 'Olivotel', 'Ved Transcube Plaza, Next to central bus terminal Vadodara', 'Olivotel is situated in Vadodara, where grand old palaces and temples juxtapose with swanky IT parks and corporate offices. The Hotel Olivotel is designed for the modern nomad, the property provides consistent, courteous and crisp service for business and leisure travellers seeking contemporary and refreshing experiences. It stands as an epitome of warm hospitality blended with the utmost luxury and comfort. Vadodara Airport and  Vadodara Junction are the nearest airport and railway station to the region.   The hotel provides places like front desk, laundry, room service, Wi-Fi and many more. In any medical emergrncy one can avail doctor on call facility. Foodies can revel in an array of enticing dishes at the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant that caters to the unique tastes of the guest. Those on business tour can host meetings, conferences and seminars. Adorned with stylish fittings, all rooms are equipped with cosy bed and clean linens and are air condition. The rooms in the hotel are well-maintained, ventilated, clean and come with good quality furniture. The hotel houses simple and sober rooms that offer a homely ambiance to guests. All rooms have attached bathroom with essential bathroom toiletries.   Experience a wonderful stay at Hotel Olivotel!', 5964, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1222, 17, 'Royal Orchid Central, Vadodara', 'Akota, Mujmahuda, Vadodara, Gujarat Akota Gardens', 'Royal Orchid Central is 2.7 km from the Vishwamitri Railway Station. It features 2,200 sq ft of event space and a stylish restaurant. The 4 star rated Royal Orchid Central is located in the business district of Vadodara. The hotel is close to the Maharaja Fateh Singh Museum and roughly 20 minutes\' drive from the Vadodara Airport. As per their budget and needs, guests can make a choice of their rooms from three types, namely Deluxe, Club and Suite. The event space in the hotel is of 2,200 sq ft and can be divided into three halls. Moreover, there is a boardroom with modern facilities that is ideal for meetings and conferences. Other than these, currency exchange, travel desk, valet parking and doctor-on-call are offered to ensure a comfortable stay of guests. PinXX is the hotel\'s stylish restaurant that serves delicious Indian and international delicacies. Guests must not miss to visit Vadodara\'s popular landmark- Kirti Stambh. This monument was built in 1935 and is approximately 10 minutes drive from the hotel.', 8619, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1223, 17, 'Yahvi UNA SMART', 'Old Padra Road', '', 9555, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1224, 18, 'Hotel Seacity Grand', 'Nh-5, Maddilapalem, Isukhathota, Nh-5 Visnu Honda Bike Showroom, SivajiPalem, VISAKHAPATNAM Sivaji Palem', 'Hotel Seacity Grand is nestled in the city of Vishakhapatnam which is a melting pot of cultures and a unique blend of the traditional and modern, welcoming discerning travelers from all over the world. It is located 14.1 km from Vishakhapatnam Airport, 5.5 km from Visakhapatnam Junction and 2.6 km from Bus Stand. The prominent tourist attractions of the city, where guests can visit are Indira Visakha Museum (3.5 km), Gandhi Zoological Park (4.8 km), Kailasagiri (5.5 km), Dr. Y.S. Rajasekhara Reddy ACA-VDCA Cricket Stadium (9 km) and Simhachalam Temple (16.6 km). Accommodation at the hotel is available in well-appointed rooms offering an imperial class and modern comfort with in-room amenities such as intercom, television, air-conditioning, mini bar, mineral water and bathroom with all essential toiletries. The array of essential services rendered by the hotel for a hassle free stay includes laundry, travel assistance, currency exchange and internet. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Hotel Seacity Grand!', 7569, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1225, 18, 'Beach View Guest House', 'opp sea pearl parlour, besides novotel hotel, rk beach main road beach road,visakhapatnam', 'Nestled in the charming city, famous for its sprawling golden beaches, splendid monuments and ancient temples, Vishakhapatnam, Beach View Guest House is a well worth property that proffers accustomed accommodation at an affordable rate. The property is an ideal spot to have funfilled stay with family and friends. The warm and supportive staff ensures any and every whim is met at the earliest. The property is located at a distance of 17.3 km from Visakhapatnam Airport, 4.4 km from Visakhapatnam Railway Station and 450 m from R.K. Beach Bus Stop. The property has an advantage as it enjoys propinquity to various popular tourist destinations like Ramakrishna Beach(1.2 km), Sub Marine Museum(1.9 km), Visakha Museum(2.6 km), Victory At Sea Memorial(2.6 km), Sri Venkateswara Temple(4.3 km) and many more. Shopaholics can indulge in shopping spree at various shopping places like CMR Shopping Mall(2 km), INOX - Chitralayaa Mall(2.4 km) and many more. To savour lip-smacking fare, guests can head to different restaurants, which are located close to the hotel. To ease the stress of travel, the hotel facilitates services like front desk and many more. The tastefully done up interiors have all the mod cons that makes a comfortable holiday for guests. The spacious, deluxe and designer rooms of the hotel invite indulgence with contemporary decor and also comfy beds and cosy bed linens. Festooned with all the facilities for comfort, the rooms are carefully designed with beautiful environs that offers necessary room amenities making stay a delightful one for guests. They have neat and clean attached bathrooms equipped with essential toiletries. Feel the Best Experience augmenting with comfort, safety, security and well being!', 5113, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
