(1290, 22, 'Hotel Mahal', 'Ferozpur road, opp. Verka milk , Ferozpur road', '|A 2 star property, Hotel Mahal is located in the city of Ludhiana. Situated 7.3 km from Ludhiana Airport, 5.4 km from Ludhiana Junction and 5 km from Ludhiana Bus Station, a luxurious budget property offers wide range services to business and leisure travelers.| Guests can visit nearby sightseeing places to the property such as Punjab Agricultural University (900 mtrs), Nehru Rose Garden (3.8 km), Gurudwara Sri Guru Singh Sabha (4.7 km) and Rakh Bagh (5.3 km).| All rooms of the property are well-furnished and equipped with modern amenities like air conditioner, cable television, intercom, direct dial phone, dining table, study table, shower area, geyser, hot/cold running water and essential bathroom toiletries.| The property offers wide range of services like laundry, taxi service, travel desk, parking, sightseeing tours, airport/railway station transfers and room service. The hotel also have well-maintained conference hall where all kind of business meetings can be arranged easily. Doctor on call facility is available for any medical emergencies in premises.| Enjoy mouthwatering and delicious regional, Indian and Continental dishes at in-house restaurant. At coffee shop, guests can enjoy their favorite flavor of coffee in serene ambiance.| Have a nice stay at the Hotel Mahal!| |less', 6964, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1291, 22, 'Hotel Nayyar Classic', 'Gurdwara Dukh Niwaran Rd, Opposite Jagraon Bridge, Field Gunj ,', '|Located in Ludhiana, Hotel Nayyar Classic is at a distance of 17.5 km from Ludhiana Airport, 1.6 km from Ludhiana Railway Station and 7.2 km from Indo Canadian Bus Stop.| Various tourist places where guest can visit like Gurudwara(450 m), Rakh Bagh Park(2.1 km), Nehru Rose Garden(4 km), Punjab Agricultural University Museum(6.3 km), Maharaja Ranjit Singh War Museum(7.1 km) and much more.| Services that hotel provides are power back-up, front desk, room service, doctor on call and laundry. Well-equipped rooms offers amenities like hot/cold water, attached bathroom and essential bathroom toiletries.| Have a comfortable stay at Hotel Nayyar Classic!| |less', 7746, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1292, 22, 'Hotel Chevron International', 'Link Road , Link Road', 'A 3 star hotel, Hotel Chevron International offers all the comforts and facilities to guests looking for a pleasant stay in Ludhiana. |Rooms| The hotel has 50 guest bedrooms across Super Deluxe, A.C. Deluxe and Suite room categories. All rooms are spacious and furnished with wall to wall carpeting. With attached bathrooms with running hot and cold running water, all the rooms have a telephone and television. The added features in the Suites are data ports, tea/coffee maker and an iron/ironing board and a refrigerator. |Dining & Facilities| The hotel\'s restaurant serves authentic Indian, Nawabi Muglai, Chinese and Continental cuisines for guests to enjoy. The Texan look Royal Bar is where guests can indulge in the choicest spirits and cocktails. Business facilities at Hotel Chevron International include two conference and banquet hall that can accommodate up to 50 persons and a Kitty Room. Other guest facilities available are safety deposit lockers, money exchange facility, car parking, doctor on call, laundry, travel desk and taxi rental. The hotel accepts all major credit cards. |Location| Hotel Chevron International is situated in the heart of the city and is walking distance from the bus stand, 2 kms from the railway station and 8 kms from the airport. |less', 8984, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1293, 22, 'The Celebrations Guest House', 'Street No3 Baba Deep Singh Nagar , Dhandra Road, Dugri', '|The Celebrations Guest House is budget property, located at an accessible distance from Airport, Railway Station and Bus Stand.| The property offers Wi-Fi connectivity, laundry service, tea/coffee maker, travel desk/car hire, 24 hours room service and in house car parking.| Sophisticatedly designed with attractive colors and textures, modern rooms of the hotel come with standard amenities and attached bathroom with hot and cold water.| The convenient site of this property makes it easy for the visitors to access popular places like Gurudwara Singh Sabha, Rakh Bagh Park, Nehru Rose Garden and Museum of Rural History of Punjab.| Have a comfortable and stupendous stay at The Celebrations Guest House!| |less', 7224, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1294, 23, 'The Oberoi Amarvilas', 'Taj East Gate Road 0.6 km from Taj Mahal', 'Just 600 metres away from the Taj Mahal, The Oberoi Amarvilas offers rooms and suites with unparallaled views of this icon of love, a spa, outdoor swimming pool, 2 in-house restaurants, multi-purpose venues and hign speed internet. The Oberoi Amarvilas is ranked 3rd on Travel + Leisure World\'s Best Awards 2015 list of Top Resorts in Asia. A magnificent 5 star property, The Oberoi Amarvilas is located 20 minutes\' drive from Agra railway station. The hotel has Mughal-inspired architecture, terraced lawns, fountains and reflection pools. Guests can choose from accommodation ranging from the Kohinoor Suite, to the Luxury Suite, Deluxe Suite with Balcony, Deluxe Suite, Premier Room with Balcony or Premier Room. In-room amenities include an LCD television, high speed WiFi, electronic safe and personal bar. Business and leisure travellers can hold conferences and high profile parties at multiple exquisite venues. Recreational facilities include a fitness centre, outdoor swimming pool, spa, luxury retail arcade and beauty parlour. There are two dining venues available for guests: Bellevue and Esphahan, which serve fine international cuisine and Indian delicacies, respectively. The Bar at The Oberoi Amarvilas is the only bar in the world to offer uninterrupted views of the Taj Mahal. Note: The swimming pool will be closed from 1st until 25th June, 2016 for maintenance.', 7124, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1295, 23, 'Courtyard by Marriott Agra', 'Taj Nagri, Phase 2, Fatehabad Road Agra', 'Hotel Courtyard Marriott Agra is a 5 star property located just 5 minutes away from the magnificent Taj Mahal serves as a perfect location for visitors. It is located 8 km from Agra Cantt Railway Station and 10.5 km from Agra Airport. The hotel offer 189 well-appointed rooms with including 18 contemporary suites. In room amenities offered are air conditioning, flat screen cable television, intercom facility, mini refrigerator, mini bar, wet bar, tea service/coffee maker, mineral water, safe in room and bathroom amenities with shower area, instant hot water, hair dryer, slippers and robe. In addition Wi-Fi internet is available on chargeable basis. Tourist destinations are easily accessible from the hotel like Agra fort (5.3 km), Shri Mankameshwar Mandir (6.6 km), Itmad-ud-Daula (8.4 km), Ram Bagh(10.4 km) and Sikandra (14 km). The hotel renders facilities like high speed internet connection, Wi-Fi, fitness center and swimming pool. Guests can savor some exotic and freshly prepared delicacies at the in-house multi- cuisine restaurant and also offers the delight of savoring an exclusive on-site dining experience. The in-house cafe is a good place to relax with friends and hobnob over a nice coffee. Relish evening drinks and spend some quality time with friends at the in-house bar. Guests can avail rejuvenating massage therapies and treatments at the in-house massage, spa. The on-site event facilities and banquet lawns is available for corporate and social meetings as well as the hotels concierge services and a 24-hour business centre. Have an unforgettable stay at Courtyard Marriott, Agra.', 9559, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1296, 23, 'Awtar Mansion', '144, SARDAR AWTAR SINGH ROAD AGRA CANTT, AGRA-282001', 'Awtar Mansion would be the most suitable for the guest to enjoy holiday. Nestled in the beautiful city of Agra, is home to the iconic Taj Mahal, a mausoleum built for the Mughal ruler Shah JahanÂ’s wife. The property is at a distance of 4 km from Agra Civil Enclave, 2 km from Idgah Railway Station and 1 km from Idgah Bus Stand. The property has an advantage as it enjoys propinquity to various popular tourist excursions like Taj Mahal (5 Km), Agra Fort (4 km), Jama Masjid (3.7 km), Tomb of Itimad ud Daulah (7.9 km) and Mehtab Bagh (9.5 km). Blend of modern architecture to give you unparalleled standard of style and sophistication with facilities like free WiFi, doctor on call, parking space, swimming pool, fitness center, business center, taxi service, guide service and airport/railway station transfer.The rooms of the hotel are spacious airy and well maintained with amenities like air conditioning, kettle, mineral water, intercom, television, lounge, safe deposit locker, dinning room, newspaper and attached bathroom with essential toiletries which makes staying here an absolute joy and ensures that the guests are well attended and their demands are met promptly. Have a wonderful stay at Awtar Mansion!', 3456, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1297, 23, 'Hotel Alleviate', '6/27, Yamuna Kinara Road Belanganj', 'Hotel Avellite, Agra is a 3 star property located in is close proximity to Agra Cantonment Railway Station (6.6 km) and Agra Airport (9.3 km). Tourist destinations are easily accessible from the hotel like Agra Fort (1.4 km), Itmad-ud-Daula (1.6 km), Ram Bagh (3.9 km), Taj Mahal (6.8 km) and Sikandra (10.5 km). The hotel proposes facilities like internet facility/ Wi-Fi, central air-conditioning, parking facility, room service, travel desk, laundry facility and doctor on call. The in-house restaurant serves a range of tantalizing dishes to suit all palates. Suitable for both corporate and leisure travellers, it features fully equipped function venues comprising conference and banquet facilities. The hotel features 45 well furnished and elegant rooms with all basic comforts like air conditioning, LED television, telephone, internet access, mini bar, daily newspaper, safety deposit locker, hair dryers, tea and coffee maker, writing desk and attached bathroom with shower and bathroom toiletries. Other comforts like iron/ironing board are made available on guests desire. Have a wonderful stay at Hotel Avellite, Agra!', 8460, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1298, 23, 'Dazzle Hotel', 'Near Jaggi Nurshing Home , Shamsabad', 'Dazzle Hotel is a 3 star property, located 14.2 km from Agra Airport, 7.1 km from Agra City Railway Station and 6.1 km from Idgah Bus Stand. While their stay at the hotel, one can visit the famous tourist attractions of the city such as Taj Mahal (2.6 km), Agra Fort (5.1 km), Jama Masjid (5.2 km) and Itimad-ud-Daulah (7.4 km). The hotel is equipped with an encore of impeccable amenities that promise luxurious and relaxed stay with warm and comfortable environment. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. A beautiful array of facilities is provided by the hotel to ease the senses and make the stay as comfortable and enjoyable as possible. With world-class amenities, the property believes in exceeding guests expectations and creating a new hospitality experience to make the stay more comfortable. Have a fun filled and relaxing stay at Dazzle Hotel!', 7294, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
