(1308, 23, 'Siris 18', '2/3 Taj Nagri Phase - II Fatehabad Road , 1.5 km from Taj Mahal', '|Siris 18 is a standard accommodation option, situated in Taj Nagri on the Fatehabad Road, Agra. The hotel is reachable within a 10-minute drive of Agra Fort Railway Station. Quality services and warm hospitality are offered at the hotel, to make the stay convenient for guests. The hotel provides necessary conveniences to suffice the varying requirements of modern day traveller. TATWA is the spa at the hotel, where guests can relax and rejuvenate. The Mokha is the on-site banquet/conference hall, which is ideal for hosting meetings and parties. Karaoke can also be enjoyed during the stay at this hotel. Internet (on request) and free parking are the other services offered here. | There are two restaurants at the hotel, where guests can relish an array of mouth-watering delicacies and delectable drinks. KuchBhi is the on-site coffee shop whereas Open Affaire is the in-house rooftop restaurant. U2 is the beer bar of the hotel, where guests can savour drinks and revel in Karoke. | The hotel offers accommodation in 31 air-conditioned rooms that are spacious and are beautifully furnished. These are divided into three categories - Deluxe Rooms (8), Super Deluxe Rooms(18) and Courtyard Rooms (5). Mini bar, cable television and direct dial telephone are the common in-room amenities. All rooms have attached bathrooms that are provided with requisite toiletries.| Begin the city expedition by visiting the Taj Mahal and Agra Fort, both of which are located close to the hotel. | |less', 4642, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
