(1358, 29, 'Hotel Sahara Aurangabad', 'Pl. No. 79, Opposite MGM hospital, Seven hill bridge road, Jalna road national highway, City : Auran Jalna Road', 'Hotel Sahara is situated in the enchanting city of Aurangabad. Located in the heart of the city the property is at a distance of 3 km from Aurangabad Airport while MIDC Railway Station is 6 km and Cidco Bus Stand is 4 km away. Some of the prominent attractions of the region lie close to this property such as Jain Temple (3 km), Bibi Ka Maqbara (6 km), Aurangabad Caves (9 km) and many other notable places. Amidst the most beautiful architecture and luxurious interiors, the hotel features various modern facilities like Wi-Fi, front desk, room service, Elevator, currency exchange and much more. The rooms in the hotel are well-maintained, ventilated and clean, and come with good quality furniture. Rooms are fitted with amenities like air condition, writing desk, tea/coffee make, television, telephone, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. Guests are in for a treat at the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant that serves lip-smacking Indian, Chinese and Continental dishes in a perfect setting. Furthermore, the hotel also features well equipped conferencing and banqueting venues, making it a perfect base for business travellers. Hotel Sahara is well-equipped to suit the needs of both business and leisure travellers!', 5441, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
