(1463, 35, 'Grand Continental Hotel', '13, Sardar Patel Marg, Civil Lines ,', '|1.3 km from Allahabad Junction, 3.4 km from Swaraaj Bhawan, 3.4 km from Jawahar Planetarium, Awarded Best Hotel in 2005 by UPHRA, Swimming pool, Wi-Fi| Situated in the heart of the city, Grand Continental Hotel is a preferred accommodation option. Designed in a contemporary style, the hotel features 47 well-designed rooms that include 6 suites. Classified as Executive Deluxe, Superior Deluxe, Studio, Suite and Executive Suite, every room is air-conditioned and has a range of amenities, including tea/coffee maker and telephone.| Ideal for business as well as leisure travellers, the hotel offers facilities like Wi-Fi, business centre, swimming pool and secretarial assistance. Two banquet halls named Imperial Suite and Viceroy Suite, a small space called Frontier and a verdant lawn are suitable venues for meetings and social gatherings.| Khana Khazana is the in-house restaurant that serves the best of local and international cuisine. Patiyala Peg - bar serves a variety of drinks is with live Gazals. Muffins - the ice-cream and confectionery shop offers different kinds of items, such as salads, pastries and sundaes.| The hotel is located within a short distance from many places of tourist interest, including Khusro Bagh and Allahabad Museum.| |less', 4097, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1464, 36, 'Pallavi International', 'Chetganj Hathwa place Chetganj', 'Located at a 10-minute drive from Varanasi railway station, Pallavi International offers free Wi-Fi, swimming pool and airport transfer facilities. Pallavi International is a 3 star hotel located in the Chetganj area of Varanasi. It is situated at a distance of 3.8 km from Varanasi City railway station. The hotel maintains spacious rooms that are equipped with amenities like air-conditioner and television. All rooms are well-decorated with paintings, depicting the rich heritage of India. This 3 star property is suitable for both holidaymakers and business travelers. For catering to the needs of corporate travelers, the hotel provides meeting facilities. Other facilities on offer include doctor-on-call, 24-hour room service, swimming pool and laundry. Pallavi International houses a multi-cuisine restaurant where guests can enjoy a range of tasty dishes. Guests must pay a visit to the Kashi Vishwanath Temple, which is at a distance of around 3.1 km from this hotel. .', 5633, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1465, 36, 'India Varanasi', '59, Patel Nagar, Cantt., Varanasi Railway Station', 'Location Offering restaurant, bar and multi-purpose hall, Hotel India is 2.9 km from Varanasi Junction and 4.5 km from Shri Kashi Vishwanath Temple.Lying close to the main railway station, Hotel India is situated in Patel Nagar, Varanasi. One of the most famous pilgrimage centre of the Hindus- Shri Kashi Vishwanath Temple is roughly 10 minutes\' drive from the hotel. Spacious and well-furnished, the rooms of the hotel are available in Standard Room, Deluxe Room, Superior Room and Suite categories. Modern amenities like cable TV, telephone and mini bar are provided in each room. During the stay, leisure travellers can avail sightseeing assistance from the on-site travel desk and explore the attractions of the city. Business travellers can utilise the multi-functional hall and well-equipped business centre to organise meetings and conferences. Laundry, Wi-Fi and airport transfer are other facilities offered at the hotel. At the on-site restaurants- Golden Dragon Restaurant and Palm Spring Restaurant, guests can savour the best of Indian, Oriental and other international dishes. Do pay a visit to the nearby Shri Kashi Vishwanath Temple, which is one of the leading shrines of the Hindus.', 9543, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1466, 36, 'Hotel Varuna', '22 Gulab Bagh, Sigra Chetganj', '1 Km from Varanasi station, 2 Km from Kashi Vishwanath Temple and 1.3 km from Kailgarh Market , Multi-cuisine restaurant, Indoor and outdoor event spaces Located within a walking distance from the IP Mall and Chakra Tal, Hotel Varuna is a 3 star establishment that offers true value for money accommodation and services. It features adequate number of rooms that are available in five options- Varuna Luxury Suite, Varuna Family Suite, Superior Rooms, Executive Rooms and Studio Rooms. Spacious and well-decorated, the rooms feature a range of amenities, including air-conditioner, LCD TV, telephone, mini bar and hair dryer. The presence of spacious indoor and outdoor venues makes the hotel an ideal venue for hosting business and party events. Preferred by both business and leisure travellers, this hotel offers many other facilities like ample space for car parking, laundry, cafe, doctor-on-call and travel assistance. Within the premises, the hotel has a stylish restaurant, which has been recently renovated. Open 27x7, this restaurant serves the best of Indian, Chinese, Italian and Continental delicacies. Proximity to the railway station, River Ganga and many important temples is the major advantage of the hotel.', 4418, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1467, 36, 'The WestInn', 'NEPALI KHOTI, THE MALL The Mall Cantonment', 'The WestInn is situated in the city of Varanasi, known for its ancient religious sites, scenic rivers, dense forests and rich culture. The property is located at a distance of 20 km from the Lal Bahadur Shastri International Airport while Varanasi Junction is 1.5 km and Varanasi Bus Stand is 2 km away.  Standing tall in the vibrant and lively streets of one of the oldest and most culturally rich cities in the country, The WestInn aims to please travellers coming in from varied parts of the world. It features a host of modern facilities like currency exchange, doctor on call, security, travel desk, first aid, parking, round the clock room service, 24 hrs power backup and laundry. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. Foodies are in for a gastronomic treat at the on-site multi-cuisine restaurant, which severs freshly prepared mouth-watering authentic delicacies.  The property makes a lasting impression as soon as one steps into the spacious rooms, which provide all expected amenities and individualistic panelling. Adorned with stylish fittings, all rooms are equipped with contemporary amenities like television, telephone, tea/coffee maker, mini-bar, In-room safe and attached bathrooms with essential bathroom toiletries. Furthermore the hotel also features well-equipped banqueting venues, making it a perfect base for business travellers.  The WestInn is a perfect place for tourists seeking spiritual and eternal peace!   ', 4329, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
