(1477, 36, 'Ganga Monastery', 'N-1/2 RM, Assi -Nagwa Near Ravi Das Ghat', 'Offering a spa and wellness centre, a massage parlour and a fitness centre, Ganga Monastery is located in Varanasi. It is 1 km from the popular Dashashwamedh Ghat. Free Wi-Fi access is available. Decorated in bright colours, the air-conditioned rooms here will provide you with a cable TV and a minibar. There is also an electric kettle. Featuring a shower, private bathrooms also come with free toiletries. At Ganga Monastery you will find a 24-hour front desk and a terrace. Other facilities offered include tour desk, laundry and luggage storage. A library is available. Currency exchange can be arranged. The property offers free parking. The famous Kashi Vishwanath Temple is 1.5 km away from the property. The Cantonment Railway Station is 4 km while the Lal Bahadur Shastri Airport is 22 km. Havens Restaurant serves Indian, Chinese, continental and Italian delights. Room service is available.', 8995, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1478, 36, 'New Hotel Broadway', 'BHU Ravindrapuri, Near I.P Vijaya Mall Crossing, Assi Ghat Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh 221001 Ravindrapuri', 'A budget property, New Hotel Broadway offers contemporary comforts at affordable prices. It is well facilitated for a pleasant stay, located 26.1 km from Lal Bahadur Shastri International Airport, 4.4 km from Banaras City Junction and 4.9 km from Varanasi Bus Stand. Guests can visit some of the various tourist places within the city such as Assi Ghat (1.4 km), Kashi Vishwanath Temple (2.2 km), Dashashwamedh Ghat (2.2 km), Manikarnika Ghat (2.6 km) and Ganges (3.3 km). Well-maintained and spacious rooms available at the property are complete with modern amenities like air-conditioning, cable television, intercom, mineral water, daily newspaper, study table, shower area, hot/cold water and bathroom with necessary toiletries. The array of essential services rendered by the hotel for a hassle free stay includes doctor on call, parking, laundry service, taxi service, guide service, sightseeing and airport/railway station transfer. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. Relish authentic and flavourful dishes in the serene ambience of the in-house swanky restaurant. It also features well-equipped conferencing and banqueting venues, making it a perfect base for business travelers. It is all about the experience that goes beyond the ordinary!', 5577, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
