(1514, 38, 'Hotel MC International', '361 Mall Road', 'Hotel Vedha is a 3 star property located in Amritsar. It is at a distance of 10 km Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport, 3 km from Amritsar Railway Station and 7 km from Indo Pak Bus Stand. The property has well equipped rooms with modern amenities like Wi-Fi access, intercom facility, ironing board, sofa unit, study table, daily newspaper, refrigerator, room heater and tea and coffee maker. Room service is available to avoid any inconvenience to the guest. Hotel facilitates laundry services, handicap facility, travel desk, railway and airport transport, guide service, business centre for personal meetings and conference hall for kitty party, birthday, ring ceremonies, marriage party and other social gathering. Doctor on call is available in any medical emergency. Vedha has a multi cuisine restaurant where one can enjoy various mouthwatering and delicious indian, chinese and continental cuisines. Hotel also has a roof top lounge and coffee shop where guest can have light tasty snacks with refreshing beverages. Popular places to visit in Amritsar are Jallianwala Bagh (6 km), Akal Takht (5 km), Durgiana Mandir (4 km), Harmandir Sahib (5 km) and many more. Have a comfortable stay at Vedha!', 4290, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(1515, 38, 'Hotel Krishnas', 'Mahna Singh road, Amritsar Mahna Singh Road', 'Hotel Krishnas is situated in Amritsar, a city with a splendid blend of tradition and culture with important religious centers and historical sites, the city reveals a magnificent past and a promising future. Guest can find various means to travel to Amritsar, Sri Guru Ram Das Jee International Airport is the nearest airport, if the guest wish to travel by train Amritsar Railway Station would be the main station in the city and there are several government-run buses and coaches operated by private companies which connects to various parts of the city. Quietly elegant and comfortable, Hotel Krishnas features facilities like doctor on call service, 24 hours of front desk service, power back up, security service. Room and housekeeping service ensures the comfortable stay of the guest long with the cleanliness of the hotel. For accommodation the hotel features capacious and spotlessly clean rooms equipped with required conveniences and these clean and ventilated rooms in the hotel are well-maintained and comes with various amenities. Guest can request for extra bed and mattress and also avail laundry service by paying an additional charge. Hotel Krishnas is an ideal pick for spending a peaceful vacation, away from the city din!', 5749, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
