(1519, 38, 'Hotel Krishna Residency', 'RB Duni Chand Road, Opp Medical College, Amritsar', 'Hotel Krishna Residency is nestled in Golden city named Amritsar. It offers a comfortable and a budget stay. It provides facilities and services for a comfortable stay to the guest. The hotel also offers facilities like Wi-Fi, doctor on call, laundry, STD/FAX/interent services, room service, 24 hour power back-up and credit card acceptance facility. For a wholesome dining experience, step in the in house multi-cuisine restaurant. Holidaymakers can avail the service of travel desk in planning a suitable itinerary as per their budget and needs. The rooms are well-equipped and well-furnished with necessary amenities like television, air-conditioning, comfortable beddings, sofa, attached bathroom with hot/water and essential toiletries. The Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport is 12.1 km, Chheharta Railway Station is 16.4 km, City Bus Stop 4 is 2.4 km away from the property. The nearby excursions that guests can visit are Hall Bazaar(2.7 km), Jallianwala Bagh(3.6 km), Golden Temple(3.9 km), Akal Takht(4 km), Durgiana temple(4.6 km) and many more. Have a pleasant stay at Hotel Krishna Residency!', 4124, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
