(1521, 38, 'Hotel Samrat', '53, Post Office Road, Court Road 2224845', 'Hotel Samrat is a budget property, located 10 km from Amritsar Airport and 2.4 km from Amritsar Junction. The prominent tourist attractions of the city, where guests can visit are Maharaja Ranjit Singh Museum (2.8 km), Durgiana Temple (3.2 km), Akal Takht (4.2 km), Harmandir Sahib (4.3 km) and Jallianwala Bagh (4.8 km). The hotel is equipped with an encore of impeccable amenities that promise luxurious and relaxed stay with warm and comfortable environment. Apart from its prime location and magnificent surroundings, the property offers a range of guest facilities, warm and personalized service backed by efficient professional and technical support, making it your dream destination for that special occasion. Have a fun filled and relaxing stay at Hotel Samrat!', 5537, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
