(1523, 38, 'Hotel Dhingra Residency', 'Opposite Escort Fortis Hospital, Verka Majitha Bye Pass Road, Greenland Verka-Majitha By Pass', 'Hotel Dhingra Residency is primarily located in the heart of the city Amritsar and offers its guests convenience to reach Airport which is just 10 km, railway station is 5 km and bus stand is 4 km away. The property is ideally situated from where Golden temple, Jallianwala Bagh, Durgiana Mandir, Ram Tirath, Wagah Border and various other tourist excursions are just nearby the hotel. With top class accommodation, the 16 well appointed rooms at the hotel have the best of amenities like air-conditioning, cable television, satellite television, intercom, Wi-Fi access, fruit basket, tea/coffee maker, mineral water, balcony/sit out, daily newspaper, fireplace, room heater, geyser in bathroom, hot/cold water and diverse other essential bathroom toiletries. A quality hotel is known for providing contemporary accommodation and facilities, which are a good blend of contemporary design and comfort with a rich cultural history and a warm hospitality providing with various facilities such as conference hall, Wi-Fi access, in-house restaurant, dining hall, round the clock room service, doctor on call, laundry, travel desk, railway station transfer, airport transfer, parking and guide service(on request). Additionally, taxi service and sightseeing is also available on chargeable basis. Savor a variety of delicious dishes at the on-site multi-cuisine restaurant, which specializes in Indian and global delicacies offering breakfast, lunch and dinner. Experience a grand stay and a warm hospitality at Hotel Dhingra Residency!', 7311, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1524, 38, 'Hotel Majha', '118, Railway Link Road, Amritsar Amritsar Railway Station', 'Hotel Majha is located in the Golden City, Amritsar. It is at a distance of 11 km from Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport, 1 km from Amritsar Railway Station and 7 km from Indo Pak Bus Stand. The property has fully furnished and spacious rooms with modern amenities like Wi-Fi access, air conditioner, LED television, tea/coffee maker and attached bathroom with regular supply of hot and cold water. Room service is available round the clock for the convenience of the guest. Hotel facilitates laundry services, power backup, round the clock security, pickup/drop services and travel desk to make tour arrangements. Popular places to visit in Amritsar are Maharaja Ranjit Singh Panorama (1 km), Maharaja Ranjit Singh Museum (2 km), Harmandir Sahib (3 km), Akal Takht (3 km), Jallianwala Bagh (3 km), Bibeksar Sahib Sarova (4 km) and many more. Have a memorable and pleasant stay at Hotel Majha!', 6474, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1525, 38, 'Hotel Namaskar', '5,Queens Road, Hotels Lane, Behind OBC Civil line Amritsar', 'Located near Amritsar Junction (1 km), Hotel Namaskar is popular with leisure travellers. Golden Temple and Jallianwala Bagh are less than 2.5 km from here.   For hassle-free travel, avail the hotels pick-up/drop and car rental services. Other facilities include conference hall, travel assistance, 24-hour room service, parking, doctor on call and internet access.   Select from the hotels air-conditioned rooms and suites that are available with cable TV, telephone, mini refrigerator, wardrobe, table, chairs and hot/cold water supply.   Savour Punjabi, Continental and Chinese dishes at the hotels restaurant. A 24-hour coffee shop is also available.   Prominent shopping hubs of the city like The Celebration Mall (2 km) and AlphaOne Mall (4 km) are a short drive away. Guests can also visit the sacred Durgiana Temple (2 km).', 6618, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
