(1527, 38, 'Temple Tower', 'Bazar Bikaneri, Nr, Jalian Wala Bagh, Jalebi Wala Chowk Bazar Bikaneri, Nr, Jalian Wala Bagh, Jalebi Wala Chowk', 'Located in Amritsar, the spiritual and cultural centre for the Sikh religion and which is known as Ambarsar, Temple Tower is in the close proximity to the religious places. It is at a distance of 13.4 km from Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport, 2.3 km from Amritsar Junction and 2.9 km from Indo Pak Bus Stand. As it is surrounded by spirituality of revered worships, those with religious interests can seek blessings here at places like Jallianwala Bagh (200 meters), Golden Temple (450 meters), Durgiana Mandir (1.5 km), Param Pujya Mata Lal Devi Mandir (4.0 km) and Tarn Taran (22.4 km). On top of that the main commercial activities include tourism, carpets and fabrics, farm produce, handicrafts, service trades, and light engineering. The air-conditioned property conveys its guests with its excellent services. Well maintained rooms of the property offers amenities like tea maker, LCD satellite television, refrigerator, iron and ironing boards and also provides amazing bath experience with hot/cold water, shower and top-drawer toiletries. It also avails electronic safe for one\'s personal belongings. As the city is known for its rich cuisine and culture, guests can visit nearby restaurants to have an fabulous experience of scrumptious foods. One can have benedictions at this profoundly honoured place with Temple Tower\'s stay....', 4435, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1528, 38, 'Hotel Raj Kanwar castle', 'Albert Rd, Putligarh Amritsar Airport Road', 'Raj Kanwar Hotel is located in beautiful city,Amritsar. The property is located at the distance of (2.4 km) from Amritsar Bus Stand,(250 m) from Amritsar Junction and (10.7 km) from Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport. Amritsar beckons with its myriad charms. Be it, the pompous ceremony by troops at the Wagah border and the dazzling opulence of the Golden Temple, or the soul stirring experience at the Jallianwala Bagh, Amritsar offers all this and much more. Amritsar is the nucleus of the Sikh religion and the lavish and legendary Golden Temple is Amritsar\'s main claim to fame. This dazzling Gurudwara sits in the midst of the holy Harmandir Sahib pool and Amritsar is named after this pool. The flawless and friendly nature of the hotel is full with all modern amenities like front desk and other needed for a relax and comfortable stay. The supportive staff of the hotel ensures that all whims of guest are timely fulfilled. The aesthetically elegant and contemporary rooms promise immaculate bed-linens and linen in addition to facilities like telephone, wardrobe and attached washroom with hot/cold water supply with essential toiletries. This property is an ideal pick for spending a peaceful vacation, away from the city din.', 5546, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1529, 38, 'Hotel K K Continental', '23, Albert Road Albert Road', 'Just a few steps from Amritsar Junction (300 m), Hotel K K Continental is popular among business and leisure travellers. It is also close to prominent attractions such as Maharaja Ranjit Singh Museum (1.4 km) and Golden Temple (2.5 km).   The hotel features a multi-purpose hall which can be booked for a private gathering or business event. Other facilities include pick and drop service, travel assistance, fax service, laundry service, parking, doctor on call, 24-hour room service, front desk and security.   Book your stay in one of the 15 rooms and suites that come equipped with air conditioning, flat-screen TV, telephone, internet access, tea/coffee maker, mini refrigerator, work desk, chair and hot/cold water supply.   Savour Indian, Chinese and Continental food at the propertys restaurant. Guests can also unwind with refreshing drinks at the lounge.   The historic Jallianwala Bagh is 3 km away. Seek blessings at the famous Durgiana Temple, about 3 km from the property.', 7846, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
