(1540, 41, 'Manhar Residency', 'Bhind Road, Atlas Tiraha , Malannpur-Bhind ,Gwalior, MP Malannpur-Bhind ,Gwalior, MP', 'Hotel Manhar Residency is a prime property located in the heart of beautiful city, Gwalior. It serves as a first choice for the travellers who are coming for either leisure or for business purpose. Hotel is located at the distance of 15 km from Rajmata Vijay Raje Scindia Air Terminal, 21 km from Gwalior Junction and is at easily accessible distance to Bus Stand. Rooms of the hotel are elegantly designed, well maintained and come with all modern day amenities like air-conditioner, television, internet facility, telephone, tea/coffee maker, daily newspaper(upon request) and much more. Attached bathrooms come with regular supply of hot/cold water plus all essential toiletries. Hotel offers wide range of facilities which ensures the stay for the guests is happy and comfortable one. Hotel provides parking facility, excellent room service and travel desk. Along with it, it also facilitates banquet hall, conference hall and meeting room so that one can organise social or business gatherings, taxi facilities, mini-bar in selected rooms, laundry services, arrangements for kitty and birthday celebration parties and much more. It houses a coffee shop where one can sip a cup of their favourite beverage along with friends or business partners. Hotel also has an in-house multi cuisine restaurant which offers mouth watering delicacies from in and around the world. Doctor on call facility can be availed at the time of medical emergency. Have a wonderful stay at Manhar Residency, Gwalior!', 9187, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(1541, 41, 'Hotel Rama Utsav', 'Utsav 7 NO, Chouraha, 1B Hariom Colony Main Road, Morar Morar', 'Hotel Rama Utsav is a budget property located in beautiful city of Gwalior. It is located at the accessible distance to Airport, Railway Station and Bus Stand. Places to visit in Gwalior are Gwalior Fort, Sas Bahu Temple, Jai Vilas Palace Museum, Gopachal Parvat and much more. Hotel provides with all modern facilities like Wi-Fi(on entire premises), safety deposit locker, travel desk, laundry service. Guests can enhance their taste buds by tasting varieties of international cuisines at multi-cuisine restaurant. One can have a conversation with friends and families over a cup of coffee at coffee shop. Moreover facilities like conference/banquet hall can be availed to organize business or social gatherings. Rooms of the hotel are very elegant and neatly designed. Amenities provided are Wi-Fi, air-conditioner, television and attached bathroom with hot/cold water and essential toiletries. Enjoy a marvellous stay at Hotel Rama Utsav.', 6547, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
