(1543, 41, 'Hotel Surbhi', 'Naya Bazar, Lashkar, Lashkar', 'Hotel Surbhi is a standard hotel offering comfortable accommodation with modern facilities to its guests. The property is at a distance of 16.2 km from Rajmata Vijay Raje Scindia Air Terminal while Gwalior Junction is 4.2 km and Gwalior Railway Station Bus Stop is 4.1 km away. Hotel Surbhi offers a plethora of facilities and services like laundry, doctor on call, Wi-Fi internet access, laundry, taxi service and credit cards are accepted for the convenience of guests. Furthermore the conferencing and banqueting space available at the hotel are ideal for organising business and social events. The property houses beautifully decorated rooms equipped with modern amenities like air conditioner, television, intercom, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. The in-house restaurant serves a range of tantalizing dishes to suit all palates. Adding to this is pleasing ambience and never ending conversations which make the stay memorable. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Hotel Surbhi!', 8944, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1544, 41, 'Hotel Balaji', 'HOTEL BALAJI  Naya Bazar,   Gwalior MP', 'A budget property, Hotel Balaji is located 126 km from Agra Airport, 4 km from Gwaior Junction and 7 km from Bus Stand. The promienent tourist attractions of the city, where guests can visit are Teli Ka Mandir (5.1 km), Sas Bahu Temple (5.7 km), Gwalior Fort (5.7 km) and Tigra Dam (17.3 km). For accommodation, the property offers spacious, airy and well-lit rooms, featuring simple decor and furnishings. They come with in room amenities like telephone and bathroom with hot water facility and essenyial toiletries. The hotel itself offers services that are designed to offer maximum comfort to its guests. Some of the services offered here are help desk, tour assistance, doctor on call and Wi-Fi. The in-house multi-cuisine restaurant dishes out the best of Indian and international delicacies to cajole the taste-buds. Those on business tour can host meetings, conferences and seminars as it features well-equipped conferencing facilities making it a perfect base for business travelers. This property is an ideal pick for spending a peaceful vacation, away from the city din!', 3723, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
