(1698, 51, 'Hotel Centre Point', 'High Ct Rd, Sri Ganganagar, Jodhpur High Court Road', 'Situated in Jodhpur, second largest city of Rajasthan in terms of population, also very close to the Thar Desert, Hotel Centre Point can be reached through various travel means, Jodhpur Airport is the closest airport(5 km) the nearest railway station is Jodhpur railway station(1.1 km) and Jodhpur has good local transport, comprising busses and autos which helps one connects to various parts of the city. Amongst the multitude of attractions here, a couple of interesting places in and around the city are Mehrangarh Fort, Jaswant Thada, Umaid Bhawan Palace Museum, Rao Jodha Desert Rock Park, Mandore Gardens. There are many restaurants situated close to the hotel, where guests can have regional and multi cuisine meals. The hotel ensures varying requirements of guests are fulfilled as ample conveniences are offered which includes housekeeping, front desk, parking and doctor on call in case of  any medical emergency. For accommodation the hotel features capacious and spotlessly clean rooms equipped with various conveniences like restful beds, clean linen, table, chairs, television and attached bathroom with hot and cold water along with essential toiletries. Hotel Centre Point is an ideal pick for spending a memorable vacation!', 6818, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1699, 51, 'Kesar Heritage', 'Mehron Ka Chowk Naya Bas', 'Kesar Heritage is a budget property, located at 5.8 kms from Jodhpur Airport, 1.7 kms from Jodhpur Junction and 1.5 kms from Station Road Bus Stand. The property offers Wi-Fi and internet, 24 hours reception, laundry, room service, taxi service, air/bus/train tickets, city guide, doctor on call, herbal massage and cooking classes. Recreation activities include camel safari, village tour and sight seeing. The rooms at the hotel are comfortable and are laced with facilities which ensure that guests enjoy their stay to the full and have a memorable outing. Some of the room amenities offered are air conditioning, television and bathroom with hot shower and toiletries. With a sole motto to pamper your taste buds, the hotel possesses the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant. The restaurant is equipped with all the modern amenities and international fixtures. It serves traditional North Indian, South Indian, Punjabi, Rajasthani, Continental, Chinese, Italian and other special dishes. The hotel is also an ideal place for those who come for sightseeing purposes as it is near to many popular places that include Mehrangarh Fort (1.8 kms), Flying Fox (1.8 kms), Rao Jodha Desert Rock Park (1.6 kms), Jaswant Thada (1.5 kms) and Umaid Bhawan Palace (5.8 kms). Experience a grand stay and a warm hospitality at Kesar Heritage!', 8593, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1700, 51, 'The Marwar Hotel And Gardens', '1. High Court Colony Residency Rd', 'Having Jodhpur\'s airport and railway station within its 3 km radius, The Marwar Hotel & Gardens features a vegetarian Indian restaurant and pool. This hotel has a swimming pool and sufficient event space. Laundry and 24-hour room service are other facilities offered to guests staying at this hotel. Jeeman, the poolside and rooftop restaurant of this hotel, serves delicious Indian cuisine. The restaurant has a variety of vegetarian dishes for guests. The Marwar Hotel & Gardens is a budget accommodation in the royal city of Jodhpur. Situated at a short drive from the Mehrangarh Fort and Umaid Bhawan Palace, this hotel is a perfect choice for leisure travelers. There are 18 AC rooms in the hotel, including three Marwar Suites, six Premium Rooms and nine Deluxe Executive Rooms. In-room amenities include internet, LCD cable television and direct-dial telephone. A mini bar is present in each of the Marwar Suites. Visit Jaswant Thada, the heritage edifice, lying about 6 km from the hotel.', 9916, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
