(1806, 59, 'Hotel City Palace', 'Plot No - 258, Bapuji Nagar Bapuji Nagar', 'Situated in Bapuji Nagar area of Bhubaneswar, Hotel City Palace offers warm hospitality and comfortable accommodation to guests. Located in proximity to Odisha State Museum, Kedareswar Temple and Rajarani Temple, this property is suitable for leisure travellers. Explore the tourist attractions in and around the city by making use of the travel desk services. To facilitate a convenient stay, it offers facilities like dry cleaning/laundry, taxi hire, power backup and medical aid. The rooms in the hotel are spacious and well-maintained, and feature comfortable bedding, side table and a separate sitting area. Essential amenities like cable TV, telephone and tea/coffee maker are some of the common amenities in rooms. These rooms also have private bathrooms with geyser and necessary toiletries. Guests can enjoy a range of lip-smacking regional and North Indian dishes at the on-site restaurant. Besides, the hotel also has a coffee shop were light snacks and refreshing drinks can be savoured. Pay a visit to the Lingaraja Temple, which is one of the oldest shrines of the city. This prominent landmark, dating back to the 11th century AD, is around a 10 minute drive from the property.', 6626, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(1807, 59, 'Atithi Bhawan', 'Plot No. 7/A Kalpana Area 751014 Kalpana Area 751014', 'About 2 km from Bhubaneswar railway station and 3.5 km from Lingaraj Temple, Atithi Bhawan offers airport transfer Situated in Kalpana Area of Bhubaneswar, Atithi Bhawan offers best value for money accommodation to travellers. The hotel features Double Non AC Rooms that are spacious and fitted with standard amenities for the convenience of guests. The attached bathrooms have essential toiletries and hot and cold water supply. Lodgers who wish to explore the several city attractions can avail car rental from the hotel. Facilities like airport transfers, power backup, doctor-on-call, parking and laundry are also provided on site so that guests can have a hassle free experience. Guests can enjoy fresh and delicious food in the cosy comfort of their rooms by availing room service. They can also head to the nearby restaurants - Country Kitchen and Green Chillyz, located within 2 km radius of the hotel. Seek blessings of Lord Shiva at the revered Lingaraj Temple, which is hardly a 10-minute drive from Atithi Bhawan or for an enriching experience visit the Odisha State Museum nearby.', 7189, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(1808, 59, 'Hotel Sandys Tower', 'P-1 & P-1/A, Jaydev Vihar , Jaydev Vihar', '|Nestled in Bhubaneshwar, a cradle of art and culture, a bustling modern city with mesmerizing temples, enchanting natural beauty and lovely people, Hotel Sandys Tower quietly elegant and exclusively offers facilities like swimming pool, board room, business centre, doctor on call facility incase of any medical emergency, travel desk. The in-house restaurant serves a range of tantalizing dishes to suit all palates and one can relish evening drinks and spend some quality time with friends at the in-house bar, which is stocked with choicest spirits. | The clean and ventilated rooms at Hotel Sandys Tower are well-maintained and comes with amenities like telephone, television, attached bathroom, hot and cold water. Room and housekeeping service ensures the comfortable stay of the guest long with the cleanliness of the hotel.| The hotel is located at a distance of 8km away from Biju Patnaik International Airport, 6.8km away from Bhubaneswar Railway Station and 1.5km away from Jaydev Vihar bus stop. Bhubaneshwar is well connected to other major cities of the country via regular buses and local vehicles.| One should make it a point to visit the famous tourist places in and around Bhubaneshwar like Museum of Tribal Arts and Artifacts(1.5km), Shree Ram Mandir(5.6km), Rajarani Temple(9.5km), Lingaraja Temple(10.4km), Nandankanan Zoological Park(10.6km) and many more.| Hotel Sandys Tower is the right choice for visitors who are searching for a combination of charm and peace!| |less', 3925, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0);
