(2021, 78, 'Ajanta Continental', '101, Rajpur Road, Dehradun - 248001, Uttaranchal, India. Rajpur', 'Hotel Ajanta Continental is located on the foothills of the Himalayas in the capital of Uttaranchal which is the beautiful and picturesque Dehradun. Ajanta Continental is an elegant hotel which offers superior comforts at reasonable prices. The hotels blend of traditional hospitality and modern facilities make it an ideal choice for business and leisure travellers. The rooms have facilities like central air conditioning, cable television, telephone and 24 hours room service. The rooms are also equipped with state of the art internet broadband connectivity. The quaint and modern bedrooms in the hotel are equipped with showers and running hot and cold water in the attached bathrooms. Atithi is the multi cuisine restaurant at the hotel which offers an exotic variety of delectable dishes. It is a perfect place to entertain your family, friends or even business associates. The hotel has as many as 4 halls for your business and informal purposes. There is Ananda Hall which is the largest pillar less venue for conventions, weddings, seminars and cocktails. It overlooks the swimming pool and can accommodate up to 500 guests. Aanchal Hall is usually used for exhibitions and seminars and can accommodate a total of 250 persons. Avantika is the small board room perfect for kitty parties and small meetings and finally Aditya Hall is the most suited venue for private parties. Have a unforgettable stay at Ajanta Continental!', 7572, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
