(2115, 84, 'Hotel Vinayak', '3 Khailand Market, Main Road Ajmer', 'Hotel Vinayak is located in the city of Ajmer. It is at an accessible distance of 135 km from the Jaipur International Airport, 750 m from the Ajmer Junction and just 1.9 km from the Ajmer Bus Stand. Popular tourists excursions such as Ana Sagar Lake (3.1 km), Taragarh Fort (4.0 km), Lake Foy Sagar (6.5 km) and many more nearby the property can be visited by the guests. Ample conveniences are offered at the hotel to suffice the varying requirements of guests. These include room service, parking, laundry service, doctor on call. Accommodation at the hotel is available well-appointed rooms, that are tastefully decorated and fitted with contemporary amenities such as telephone, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries to make the stay comfortable for the guests. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks assistance. Adding to this is a pleasing ambience and never-ending conversations which will sum up to a memorable experience. Have a relaxed stay at Hotel Vinayak!', 7260, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(2116, 84, 'Hotel Chitvan', 'Jaipur Road, Near Akashwani, P.O. Gagwana P.O. Gagwana', 'Hotel Chitvan is located in Ajmer. It is at a distance of 19 km from Kishangarh Airport, 13 km from Ajmer Railway Station and 11 km from Ajmer Bus Stand. Popular tourist attractions in Ajmer are Anasagar Lake (16 km), Taragarh Fort (17 km), Foy Sagar Lake (19 km), Ajmer Sharif (14 km), Pushkar Fort (30 km), Raghunatha Swamy Temple (25 km), Adhai Din Ka Jhopra (14 km), Nasiyan Temple (13 km) and many more. Hotel facilitates garden area, swimming pool, taxi services, handicap facilities, outdoor activities, business facilities for official meetings, and conference hall for kitty party, birthday party, ring ceremony and social gathering. Chitvan has multi cuisine restaurant where one can enjoy mouthwatering and delicious south indian, north indian and chinese cuisines. Guest will have the feeling of having authentic dishes and enjoy their feast to the fullest. The property has uniquely decorated and stylish rooms with modern amenities like Wi-Fi access, air conditioner, intercom facility, television, tea and coffee maker and spacious en suit bathroom with geyser. Room service is available to avoid any kind of inconvenience to the guest. Have comfortable stay at Hotel Chitvan!', 8462, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2117, 84, 'Hotel Kanak Sagar', 'Bhainsa Complex, Prithvi Raj Marg, Ajmer. Khailand Market', 'Only 800 m from Ajmer Junction, Hotel Kanak Sagar is a preferred choice among business and leisure travellers. Akbar Fort (260 m), Gol Pyau (350 m) and Nasiyan Temple (450 m) are within walking distance.   It offers 24-hour front desk, airport/railway station transfers, car rental, tour assistance, meeting and banquet halls, laundry service, parking, and 24-hour power back-up.   Featuring a private balcony, all rooms and suites are well-equipped with air conditioning, television, telephone, wardrobe, work desk, sofa set (select rooms), and 24-hour hot/cold running water supply.   The hotels Pehli Manzil Restaurant offers Indian cuisine. 24-hour room service is also available.   Dargah Bazar (650 m), Ajmer Sharif Dargah (1.1 km) and the 12th-century Adhai Din Ka Jhonpra (1.5 km) are must-visit attractions of the city. You can also plan a day trip to the holy town of Pushkar (13 km).', 4579, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(2118, 84, 'Hotel Sobhraj', 'Dargh Road Ajmer Dargah Road', 'A budget property, Hotel Sobhraj is located at a distance of 136 km from Sawai Mansingh International Airport, 1.8 km from Ajmer Junction and 2.2 km from Ajmer Bus Stand. The hotel is in the close proximity to various tourist places like Sony Ji Ki Nasiya(450 m), Akbari Masjid(900 m), Dargah Shariff(1 km), Ana Sagar Lake(2.3 km) and Pushkar Fort(15 km). The hotel has a travel desk and offers car rental service. Other facilities available at the hotel include railway station/bus stand transfers on request, laundry & dry cleaning service, doctor on call and spacious parking. The hotel serves a range of delectable Indian and Chinese dishes through room service. The hotel offers comfortable accommodation in well furnished rooms. Each room is equipped with a telephone and television while the attached wash room is appointed with all required amenities and receives a continuous supply of hot and cold water. Hotel Sobhraj offers all modern facilities at affordable prices.', 6806, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0);
