(2286, 100, 'Jag Niwas Guest House', '21,ghangour ghat marg, Lake Pichola', 'Nestled in the royal city that possess a splendid style in recreation and entertainment, Udaipur, Jag Niwas Guest House is a dazzling property. Guests are welcomed in the hotel with warm interiors, surrounded by tasteful furnishings, coupled with the personalised services that makes the stay a pleasurable one for guests.  For a relaxed and comfortable stay, the hotel features facilities like Wi-Fi, front desk, laundry and room service. For immediate care of guests, doctor on call facility is also available. The combination of the modern lavish interior and the scrumptious food of the restaurant attracts guests and makes their experience so pleasure and memorable. An epitome of warm hospitality, efficient and polite staff of the hotel makes feel at home. The rooms offers harmonious blend of elegance, luxury and offer exclusivity with timeless style and grace. All rooms are replete with essential room amenities like television, air conditioning, attached bathrooms equipped with essential bathroom amenities and toiletries along with hot/cold water supply. The property is located at a distance of 23.5 km from Maharana Pratap Airport while Udaipur Railway Station is 3.5 km and Udaipur City Bus Station is 2.8 km away. One can visit various tourist attractions like Jagadish Temple(140 m), City Palace(350 m), Lake Pichola(100 m), Fateh Prakash Palace(1.7 km) and many more in their leisure time. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Jag Niwas Guest House!', 3354, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(2287, 100, 'Osheen Palace', '147, Machala Manga, Opp Paras Cinema Paras Cinema', 'Osheen Palace in Udaipur is 1.4 km from Udaipur City Railway Station, 2.3 km from Roadways Bus Stand and 23.7 km from Maharana Pratap Airport. Expedition places in near vicinity of the property are Gulab Bagh Zoo(2.1 km), Jagmandir(2.4 km), Taj Lake Palace(2.6 km), Jagadish Temple(2.7 km), Lake Pichola(2.7 km), City Palace(2.8 km), Shiv Niwas Palace(3.2 km), Saheliyon Ki Bari(6.0 km), Moti Magri(6.5 km), Fateh Sagar Lake(6.9 km) and Monsoon Palace(10.2 km). The hotel offers the facilities like Wi-Fi internet, laundry service, travel desk and parking facility with room service to its guests for comfortable and memorable stay. It also offers business centre to the business travellers which can be used to organise business meetings. Rooms of the property are spacious, clean and well equipped with with cable television, Wi-Fi internet, study table, tea/coffee maker and refrigerator. The hotel houses an in-house restaurant that serves a wide array of traditional Rajasthani style cooking that will pamper appetite of guests. Enjoy your stay at Osheen Palace!', 3476, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2288, 100, 'Garden Hotel', 'OppSajjan Niwas Garden Lake Palace Road', 'Nestled in the City of Lakes, The Garden Hotel is located at a distance of 22.0 km from Maharana Pratap Airport, 2.2 km from Railway Station Udaipur and 650 m from Roadways Bus Stand. The eminent tourist excursions suchlike Jagmandir(2.0 km), City Palace(2.4 km), Taj Lake Palace(2.6 km), Chamunda Mata Temple(4.1 km) are situated in the close vicinity to the hotel. Quietly elegant and exclusive, the hotel features facilities suchlike parking, Wi-Fi internet access, business center and laundry service. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. The rooms here are designed to provide comfort with amenities like air-conditioning, television, telephone, wardrobe, hot/cold water and attached bathroom with essential toiletries. Come enjoy and relax with your family and friends at The Garden Hotel!', 9720, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0);
