(2291, 100, 'Hotel Rajkamal international', '123 Bye pass Road, Bhuwana Udaipur', 'Hotel Rajkamal international is a budget property located in the lakecity Udaipur. It is at a distance of 21.6 km from Maharana Pratap Airport, 9.9 km from Udaipur Railway Station and 8.7 km from Bus Stand.The hotel offers facilities like power backup, car service, ticket reservation, internet facility and tour guide. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks help. Saheliyon Ki Bari (5 km), Udaipur Solar Observatory (6 km), Fateh Sagar Lake (6.6 km), Shilpgram (7.2 km), Jagadish Temple (7.7 km), City Palace of Udaipur (7.9 km), Bagore Ki Haveli (8.4 km), Vintage Collection of Classic Cars Museum (8.8 km), Jag Mandir (10.5 km) and Lake Pichola (10.8 km). Guests can choose to stay in spacious and well-maintained rooms that are provided with all essential conveniences to make the stay pleasurable for guests. With clean and hygenic neighbourhood, the rooms feature simple decor, furnishings and amenities like television, telephone and attached bathrooms with hot/cold running water and essential bathroom toiletries. The multicusine restaurant serves choicest dishes from around the world to cater to the varied taste of travellers. The hotel features a large conference hall for business travellers to host business meetings, seminars and conferences. Have a pleasant stay at Hotel Rajkamal international!', 9731, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
