(2293, 100, 'Amar Kothi', 'Haridas Ji ki Magri, Near Oberoi Udai Vilas, Udaipur, Rajasthan 313001 Haridasji Ki Magri', 'As the name suggest Hotel Amar Kothi is a traditional haveli mansion enhanced with modern style & luxury. We are located at the Haridas ji ki Magri which is very peaceful & posh area of Udaipur. All the major tourist attractions and shopping areas are just 15 minutes away from Hotel Amar Kothi. The hotel also gives you a feel of a homestay, so that feel like at home only. Our dedicated staff is very friendly, always ready to serve & help you.Hotel Amar Kothi has magnificent architecture and a soothing ambiance. While your stay at Hotel Amar Kothi you can enjoy the marvelous view of the Pichola lake, Lake Palace, City Palace Complex, Sajjan Garh - Monsoon Palace, Neemach mata hilltop temple, Karnimata mata hilltop temple, Old & new city areas and surrounding Aravalli hills. Our Restaurant is very nice & cozy, offers various delicious delicacies from continental to Rajasthani. Other highlights includes mirror inlayed, wodoon carving, ample parking, easily accessible, spacious rooms.', 8550, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(2294, 100, 'Janak Niwas Guest House', '15 Sahiwalo ki gali, Bhatiyani Chotta City Palace', 'A budget property, Janak Niwas Guest House is located 23.5 km from Maharana Pratap Airport, 2.9 km from Udaipur City Railway Station and 5.8 km from Bus Stnad. Guests can visit some of the famous tourist attractions of the city such as City Palace of Udaipur (400 m), Bagore Ki Haveli (450 m), Lake Pichola (1.6 km), Lake Fatehsagar Udaipur (3.2 km) and Dharohar (4.9 km). Accommodation at the property is available in well-appointed rooms, that are tastefully decorated and fitted with contemporary amenities such as telephone and attached bathroom with shower and essential toiletries. The guest house itself offers services that are designed to offer maximum comfort to its guests. Some of the services offered here are laundry, doctor on call, travel desk, parking and car rental. Have a fun filled and relaxing stay at Janak Niwas Guest House!', 4567, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(2295, 101, 'Hotel Royal Fort', 'Behind Hotel Pola Paradise, New Trunk Road Bellary', 'Recognised as a pioneer amongst luxury hotels located in the Bellary, Royal Fort offers delectable cuisines at its multi-cuisine restaurant along with fully loaded bar and internet facility. Conveniently located in front of Asia\'s 2nd biggest mono lithic rock carved with Tipu Sultan Fort on it, the hotel offers elegantly appointed accommodation in 40 rooms equipped with upgraded amenities. With a well attentive room service and laundry, each room has sufficient area and comes with tea/coffee maker, data port, DVD player, refrigerator and mini bar on request in all rooms. Similarly, all private bathrooms come with upgraded fittings and have bath tub, shower area and running hot/cold water. The hotel also consists of a modernised business center and a conference venue to facilitate corporate clients. The hotel is located 33.5 km from Vidyanagar Airport, 29 km from Toranagallu Railway Station and 4.1 km from Bellary City Bus Stand. Tourist attractions to visit in Bellary are Vijayanagara, Royal Enclosures, Lakshmi Narasimha Temple, Mahanavmi Dibba, Bellary Fort and Radhika Theatre. An ideal place to relax and rejuvenate, away from the hustle-bustle of the city life.', 4075, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
