(2554, 146, 'Hotel KBN', 'Station road, Bhuj-Kachchh 370001 Gujarat', 'Hotel KBN is located 4.2 km from Bhuj Airport, 2.1 from Bhuj Railway Station and 700 m from Bhuj City Bus Stand. Major tourist attractions are Kutch Museum(1.1 km), Aina Mahal (1.2 km), White Desert(1.5 km), Shree Swaminarayan Temple Bhuj(1.6 km), Bhujia Fort(1.9 km), and many more are worth visiting within the vicinity. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks help. The hotel offers Wi-Fi, doctor on call, laundry facilities, guide and taxi on hire, parking, housekeeping and all major credit card accepted. The property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. Guest can also avail the facility of campfire and barbecue on request. The hotel also provides a multi-cuisine restaurant to enrich the taste-buds. The rooms in the hotel are well-maintained, ventilated and clean, and come with good quality furniture along with the amenities like, direct dialing from room, television, attached bathroom with hot/cold water and essential toiletries. This property is an ideal pick for spending a peaceful vacation, away from the city din!', 3714, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2555, 146, 'City The Village Resort', 'MES Road, Madhapar, Bhuj', 'City The Village Resort is traditional luxury property nestled right in the heart of Bhuj. The property is at a distance of 8.3 km from Bhuj Airport while Bhuj Railway Station is 5.6 km and Bhuj City Bus Stand is 4.1 km away. The property offers traditional living style, impeccable services, optimum benefits and and a way to get away from the humdrum of modern, fast life. The resort offers facilities like round the clock room service, swimming pool, doctor on call, Wi-Fi access, travel desk, laundry, parking and front desk. The rooms here are designed to provide comfort with amenities such as air condition, LCD television, direct dial phone, kettle, mini refrigerator, hair dryer, iron/ironing board, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. The resort houses a restaurant which is made up of the finest wood and glass overlooking the swimming pool and lush green lawn, It serves astronomical delights like Punjabi, Chinese, Mexican and Italian cuisines to pamper varied taste of traveller. City The Village Resort also has a cafe where guests can enjoy mouth freshening mock tails, different varieties of coffees and non alcoholic beverages.City The Village Resort is an oasis of peace and tranquillity!', 4647, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
