(2558, 146, 'Shree Krishna Holiday Resort', 'Opp Railway Station, Village Kukma,  Tal Bhuj-Kutch  Gujarat, India Bhuj', 'Located in Bhuj, Shree Krishna Holiday Resort is at an accessible distance from the airport and railway station. The rooms of the hotel are spacious airy and well maintained which makes staying here an absolute joy. The hotel also offers room service, parking and garden which ensures that the guests are well attended and their demands are met promptly. Guest can have a refreshing dip at the in house swimming pool. Have a fun-filled stay at Shree Krishna Holiday Resort!', 7231, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(2559, 146, 'Hotel Seven Sky', 'Seven Sky Ring Road', '3.5 km from Harmirsar Lake, 4.5 km from Bhuj Railway Station, 4.5 km from Bhuj Bus Stand. Centrally situated in the city of Bhuj, Hotel Seven Sky houses a large swimming pool and a conference hall. It also features a multi-cuisine restaurant. Including air conditioning, all rooms at Hotel Seven Sky come fitted with cable TV and intercom facility. Wi-fi access is available. Guest can sample the finest selection of dishes at the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant. Room service is offered for an added comfort. Hotel Seven Sky also features a well-equipped conference hall. Free parking is provided. Other facilities include railway/airport transfer, doctor on call and laundry service. Taxi services are provided at a charge.', 9003, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
