(2561, 146, 'Kutch Safari Lodge', 'Near Rudramata dam , Khavda road', '|Located in the outskirts of Bhuj Kutch Safari Lodge is a sprawling property set against the beautiful backdrop of the Rudramata Dam. Enjoy your evenings looking at the scenic view from the lawns and you will be charmed for life. Kutch Safari Lodge features 17 Bhunga Cottages carefully crafted after the traditional Kutchi homes. All the cottages are air-conditioned and decked with attached bathroom and amenities. | Attractions like Aina Mahal Museum, Prag Mahal Palace are closely located while the famous weavers village of Bhujodi and Mandvi Beach are a short drive from the hotel. Even the Great Rann Of Kutch is about an hours drive from the hotel but the good road condition makes your journey a smooth one. Guests are offered a 24-hour room service, doctor on call, laundry taxi service, transfers and parking. Best suited for leisure travelers, the Kutch Safari Lodge is very proactive in helping you plan your day. | You can also unwind and relax at the outdoor swimming pool. There are a few indoor games available apart from the cultural and folk programs that can be organised on request. Dining at the Banni, their in-house restaurant is a sheer treat courtesy the delicious Indian and Continental dishes it serves. | Do not forget to ask for jeep safari or full day village tour at the travel desk! | |less', 8015, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
