(2567, 148, 'Minerva Grand', 'Near Railway Flyover,Next to Reliance Mart, Renigunta Road Renigunta Rd', 'Around 2.2 km from Tirupati Main Railway Station, Hotel Minerva Grand offers a multi-cuisine restaurant, doctor-on-call facilities and Wi-Fi access. Located just few minutes drive from the main railway station, Hotel Minerva Grand is an ideal choice for travellers visiting Tirupati city. This 3 star hotel features 69 well-decorated rooms that are categorised as Premium Rooms, Imperial Rooms and Grand Suite. In-room amenities include television, Wi-Fi connection, mini bar, tea/coffee maker and safety deposit locker. This hotel is perfect for both corporate and leisure guests, owing to its myriad services that include currency exchange, laundry, doctor-on-call and valet car parking. Guests can enjoy authentic Indian and international dishes, along with choicest drinks, at the on-site Blue Fox Bar and Restaurant. Do not miss to visit the famous Govindaraja Swamy Temple that is 9 km away from this hotel. .', 5804, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2568, 148, 'Poojith Residency', '19 - 3 - 34, Opp RTC Bus Stand Near Ambedkar Circle Tirupati APSRTC Central Bus Station', 'Poojith Residency, situated within 2 km radius of Tirumala Venkateswara Temple, features a restaurant and three multi-purpose halls. Located near the bus stand, Poojith Residency is a 2 star property that offers comfortable accommodation to travellers visiting Tirupati. Major tourist attractions of the city, such as ISCKON Temple and Sri Venkateswara Museum, are located in the vicinity of the hotel. It features 50 spacious rooms that include 34 Double Bed Rooms, 11 Deluxe Rooms and 5 Suite Rooms. Every room has necessary amenities required for a comfortable stay. With a prime location and standard facilities, the hotel ably caters leisure as well as business travellers. It has three multi-purpose halls for parties and meetings. Other facilities offered by the hotel include laundry, power backup and doctor-on-call. Guests can relish a wide range of dishes at the in-house restaurant that has a relaxed setting. Do visit the iconic Tirumala Venkateswara Temple nearby, one of the main tourist attractions of Tirupati.', 4765, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(2569, 148, 'Hotel Harsha Residency', 'Near Tirupati Railway Station, RC Road, Near Palani Theatre Tirupati Railway Station', 'Within walking distance from Tirupati railway station (600 m), Govinda Raja Swamy Temple (450 m) and Govindarajula Swamivari Temple (900 m), Hotel Harsha Residency is popular with spiritual travellers. The hotel offers facilities such as doctor on call, photocopying, internet access, laundry service and parking. Sightseeing tours and railway station transfers are also arranged on request. Stay in rooms and suites that are equipped with comforts such as air conditioning, LED TV, telephone, tea/coffee maker, personal safe and 24-hour room service. You can enjoy tea/coffee and meals in the comfort of your rooms. For flavoursome chicken biryani, you may walk to the nearby Carrots Restaurant (650 m). Plan a visit to Sri Venkateswara Zoological Park (7 km) to see white tiger and barking deer. The famous Kapila Theertham is about 4 km away', 3497, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2570, 148, 'Hotel Sree Vaibhav Residency', '60044/157C,P.K.Layout Tirupati APSRTC Bus Stand', 'Located within a km from Tirupati railway station, Hotel Sree Vaibhav Residency offers travel assistance and room service Located in the heart of the city at just a 5 minutes walk away from the Tirupati Central Bus Station, Hotel Sree Vaibhav Residency is a popular budget hotel in Tirupati. Several tourist attractions, including the famous Padmavathi Ammavari Temple and Tirumala Venkateswara Swamy Temple are located within easy access from this hotel. It offers spacious and well-furnished rooms that are equipped with necessary amenities like air-conditioner, telephone, cable television and attached bathroom. The hotel\'s location close to the prominent attractions as well as the railway station makes it ideal for leisure travellers. It provides parking facility and has a travel desk for providing sightseeing assistance. Guests can enjoy delicious meals served in the comfort of their rooms through prompt room service. Also, they can dine at nearby restaurants like Hot Touch and Dakshin. Do visit Padmavathi Ammavari Temple, which is just a 10-minute drive away from the hotel.', 5970, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0);
