(2641, 161, 'Hotel Surya Vilas Palace', 'Bharatpur Bharatpur', 'Hotel Surya Vilas Palace is situated in Bharatpur. The property is situated at a distance 50.8 km from Agra Airport while Bharatpur Junction is 9.7 km and Krishna Nagar Bus Stand is 6 km away. The hotel is constructed in the Mughal style of architecture with all modern facilities, but with the ambience of a Heritage Hotel set in spacious gardens. The facilities provided here are front desk, concierge, travel desk, car rental, currency exchange, business centre, doctor on call, fitness club, parking and round the clock room service. Furthermore the hotel features well-equipped conferencing and banqueting venues, making it a perfect base for business travellers. Every room in the hotel is uniquely designed with cozy interiors and offer exclusive amenities like air condition, satellite television, telephone, balcony, Tea/coffee maker, mini bar, hair dryer, shower, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. Guests can avail rejuvenating massage therapies and treatments at the in-house spa. A scrupulously clean and extremely comfortable gym for fast, convenient and affordable workout is also available for guests to exercise and stay fit during their stay. Foodies are in for a gastronomic treat at the on-site restaurant, which severs mouth-watering vegetarian and non-vegetarian delicacies. Adding to this is a pleasing ambience and never-ending conversations which will sum up to a memorable experience. Guests can relish evening drinks and spend some quality time with friends at the in-house bar, which is stocked with choicest spirits overlooking the swimming pool and the glorious golden sunsets of the hotel. Experience a grand stay and a warm hospitality at Hotel Surya Vilas Palace!', 7031, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2642, 161, 'Udai Vilas Palace', 'NH - 11, Fatehpur Sikri Road Fatehpur Sikri Road', 'Set amidst 2 acres of lush greenery, Udai Villas Palace is located on the main Bharatpur-Fatehpur Sikri Road, right in the heart of Bharatpur city. The Keoladeo National Park, one of the prominent bird sanctuaries of the country, can be reached in just a 5-minute drive from here. After a tiring day, guests can relax in the outdoor swimming pool or revitalise themselves at the well-equipped gymnasium on site. The hotel also offers table tennis and lawn tennis facilities along with steam, sauna and Ayurvedic massages. Sightseeing excursions in and around the city, village jeep safaris and shopping tours can be arranged by the property upon request. Other facilities provided to guests include round-the-clock room service, laundry and medical aid. Ghosla, the multi-cuisine restaurant of the hotel, serves authentic Rajasthani, Chinese and Continental delicacies. At the well-stocked bar, enjoy a laid back evening sipping exotic drinks. For accommodation, it has 50 elegantly furnished rooms and suites that have colonial style decor. These rooms have comfortable bedding and feature essential amenities like direct dial telephone, television and mini bar. En suite bathrooms have hot/cold running water facility and are fitted with bathtubs. Guests can enjoy enthralling music and folk dance performances organised by the hotel.', 6685, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
