(2817, 207, 'Hotel Royale Park', 'YMCA ALLEPPEY', 'Hotel Royale Park is a classic property situated in the city of Allepey, a hub of Kerela\'s Backwaters. The property is located at the distance of 3.4 km from Alappuzha Railway Station, 1.1 km from Alappuzha KSRTC Bus Stand and at an accessible distance from an Airport. Hotel Royale Park offers its guests easy access to quite a few attractions like Ravi Karunakaran Museum(1.3 km), Alappuzha Light House (2.4 km), Vijay Beach Park (2.4 km), Alappuzha Beach (2.7 km) and Marari Beach Resort (13 km). It offers travel desk for guests who want to explore the city can avail sightseeing. The property facilitate parking space, conference hall, business hall, banquet hall, safe locker, beer and wine parlor, doctor on call, pickup and drop facility, credit and debit card facility. The multi cuisine restaurant serves choicest dishes from around the world to cater to the varied taste of travelers. The property offer a blend of luxury and affordability while choosing rooms. Well-maintained and spacious rooms available at the property are complete with modern amenities like Wi-Fi, hot and cold water, laundry service, newspaper, room service. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Hotel Royale Park !', 9414, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(2818, 207, 'Riverland Silverlines Houseboat', 'palluthuruthy Narayanapuram', 'Riverland silverlines Houseboat is nestled in the land of exotic backwaters! Packed with alluring serenity and mesmerizing beauty, Alleppey. It is a perfect place to enjoy a laidback vacation.   The popular tourist spots suchlike Nehru Trophy Finishing Point Stadium, Mullackal Rajarajeswari Temple, Alappuzha Beach, Ambalappuzha Sri Krishna Temple, Pathiramanal Island and many others are situated in the close vicinity. Hotel is easily accessible from Alappuzha Railway Station and KSRTC bus Stand and Cochin International Airport is the nearest airport.   For a comfortable and a laid back stay, the houseboat offers facilities such as front desk, housekeeping, doctor on call service, complimentary breakfast, and 24/7 Power supply. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely.   Plush accommodation is featured in ultra luxurious houseboats within room amenities like restful beds, air condition, television, table, chairs and wardrobe. Additionally a spacious bathroom equipped with hot/cold running water all through the trip and sparking clean fitting.   Have a fun filled and relaxing stay at Riverland Silverlines Houseboat Allepey!', 6029, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0);
