(3049, 291, 'Hotel Suhim Portico', 'Helipad Road, Near District Administrative Centre,Upper Sichey Gangtok', 'Located minutes away from the capital city of Gangtok, the hotel offers comfortable accommodation in well-furnished rooms, equipped with cable TV, intercom facility, and tea/coffee maker. The hotel facilities include transfers and travel desk. The hotel is approximately 125 kms. from the Bagdogra Airport, and 120 kms. from the New Jalpaiguri Railway Station. Hotel Facilities Internet Access | Taxi Services (chargeable) | Railway Station Transfer/Airport Transfer | Travel Desk | Parking Facility | Laundry Service (chargeable) | Doctor on Call | Conference Hall Room Amenities Cable TV | Intercom Facility/ Direct Dial Telephone | Snack Basket | Fruit Basket | Mini Bar (chargeable) | Tea/Coffee Maker | Daily Newspaper | Study Table | Sofa Unit | Dining Table | Piped/Channel Music | Geyser in Bathroom | Hot & Cold Water | Bathroom Toiletries Suites also have Living Room in addition to above facilities. DVD Player and Room Heater are available on request, and are chargeable. The hotel offers Double Deluxe rooms. Room service is available 24 hours. Dining The hotel has an indoor restaurant, and a bar. Internet: Available | Parking Facility: Available Check-In Time: 12:00 Noon | Check-Out Time: 12:00 Noon', 9681, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3050, 291, 'Hotel Oak Ridge', 'below district court,sichey Gangtok', 'Nestled in the eminent Buddhist pilgrimage centre, an amicable cultural fusion, Gangtok, The Oak Ridge Retreat is a charming property. It proffers luxury and budget travellers a convenient and friendly accommodation. It is an ideal destination for a while to relax and replenish spirit. The nearest airport and railway station to the region is Bagdogra Airport and New Jalpaiguri Junction Railway Station. Guest can opt for various means of transport like taxis and other road transports to travel to reach the property. The property features Wi-Fi, front desk, laundry, doctor on call and many more. The well-trimmed lawn here provides an opportunity to stage celebratory occasions under the infinitely stretched cover of the sky. The multi-cuisine all-day dining restaurant, offers an eclectic array of culinary delights from around the world. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. The hotel features quite capacious, airy and well lit rooms that come with comfy beds and cosy bed linens. Every room in the hotel is uniquely designed with cozy interiors and offer standard amenities like television, work desk and many more. All guest rooms are attractively furnished and decorated. Attached bathrooms here are fitted with essential toiletries. Ease out and have a relaxed stay at The Oak Ridge Retreat!', 9004, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
