(3061, 315, 'THENGAL MANOR', 'Jalukanibari, Na Ali, Jorhat', 'Thengal Manor is the majestic mansion in Jorhat. The property is at a distance of 8 km from Jorhat Airport and Jorhat Town Railway Station is 1.9 km away. Jorhat is and has been a vibrant place and is a perfect mixture of tradition and modernity. The property offers you the unique pleasure of gracious living in the lap of nature. Quietly elegant and exclusive the property offers facilities such round the clock room service, swimming pool, indoor games, croquet, fishing, parking and front desk for making the stay memorable for guests. Facilities like laundry, doctor on call, conference facility and airport transfer can be availed on chargeable basis. Feel the ambiance of colonial days as you relax in the period furniture and decor in all rooms. The rooms are fitted with amenities such as television, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. It also offers fireplaces in all the bedrooms, drawing room and the dining room. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Thengal Manor!', 3675, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3062, 315, 'Hotel Earl Grey', 'Tarajan,Bye-Pass,Kotoky Pukhuri Near Ajanta Cinema Hall Jorhat-785006, Assam ,', '|Hotel Earl Grey, is located at an accessible distance from Airport, Railway Station and Bus Stand. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour help.| The hotel offers facilities like parking, front desk, doctor on call and room service. For accommodation, the property offers spacious, airy and well-lit rooms, featuring simple décor, furnishings and amenities like air conditioning, television, intercom and bathroom with essential bathroom toiletries.| Have a nice stay at Hotel Earl Grey!| |less', 6345, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3063, 315, 'Hotel MDs Continental', 'Hotel MDs, Marwaripatty ,', '|Location| Hotel MD\'s Continental is located in Marwaripatty, Old Balibat, Jorhat, and is approximately 7 km from the Jorhat Airport, and 1 km from the Jorhat Railway Station. |Hotel MD\'s Continental is a 3-star property that offers visitors to Jorhat an ideal and convenient location to enjoy comfortable accommodation, a host of facilities and services, as well as warm hospitality.| |Rooms| The rooms at Hotel MD\'s Continental are comfortable and spacious, complete with modern amenities. Rooms are divided into the following categories: Deluxe (30 rooms), Executive (8 rooms), and Suite (2 rooms). In-room amenities include: cable television, telephone, tea/coffee maker, broadband internet access, fruit basket, mineral water, room heater, and an attached washroom with hot/cold water and bath tub. 24 hour room service is also available. |Dining| Hotel MD\'s Continental has an excellent multi-cuisine restaurant called |Suruchi| that serves a wide variety of delicious and wholesome dishes. The hotel also has a well-stocked bar called |Surror|, as well a sweets and snacks counter. |Facilities| Hotel MD\'s Continental offers a range of facilities and services to its guests, including: 2 conference halls, 1 banquet hall called |Milan|, a business centre, travel desk, gymnasium, as well as taxi services, laundry services, housekeeping, and a doctor on call. |less', 9675, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3064, 318, 'Hotel Jessul Kot', '17, Bhaskar Street, Near Geeta Ashram Near Geeta Ashram', 'Hotel Jessul Kot in Jaisalmer is 4.0 km from Jaisalmer Airport, 3.0 km from Railway Station and 2.3 km from Main Bus Stand. Palces travellers can visit are Nathmal Ji Ki Haveli(600 m), Vyas Chhatri(650 m), Patwaon-Ki-Haveli(700 m), Jaisalmer Fort(1.2 km), Baba Ramdev Ji Ka Mandir(1.6 km), Desert Cultural Centre(2.3 km), Amar Sagar(11.1 km) and Bada Bag(12.3 km).The hotel features facilities like parking and travel desk. Guests can avail the facility of doctor on call in case of any medical emergency. In-house restaurant serve delicious cuisines to pamper appetite of the guests. Rooms of the property are well designed, spacious and clean. Rooms have air-conditioner, cable television, intercom, dinning table, sofa unit and study table. Attached bathroom have shower area, geyser and bathroom toiletries. Mineral water and daily newspaper are available on request. Have a nice and refreshing stay at Hotel Jessul Kot!', 9522, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3065, 318, 'The Chirag Desert Camp', 'Near Parking Toll Gate, Sam Sam', 'Situated in the Sam Sand Dunes of Pink City Jaisalmer, the Chirag Desert Camp is a 3 star property. The Camp site offers luxurious accommodation to make sure guests enjoy their stay in the beautiful desert away from the hustle bustle of daily routine. Nearest railway station to the property is Jaisalmer Railway Station located at the distance of 147 km. While enjoying stay at the campsite, guests visit famous places of Sam Sand Dunes(2.9 km), Patwon-Ki-Haveli(37.6 km), Jaisalmer like Jaisalmer Fort(38 km) and Gadi Sagar Lake(38 km). The elegantly designed rooms present contemporary elegance and convenience. Each room features a dining table, Hot/cold running shower and essential bathroom toiletries. The property offers services like mobile camping, jeep safari, sand therapy, folk dance, travel counter, taxi service, camel ride, gala dinner, guide service and room service. Doctor on call facility is available to attend any medical emergencies. The multi-cuisine restaurant of the hotel has a perfect setting where guests can enjoy scrumptious regional, Chinese and Continental dishes. Have a memorable and funfilled stay at the Chirag Desert Camp!', 6475, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
