(3069, 318, 'Hotel Heera Court', 'Dr.Achalvanshi colony Near Geeta Asharm circle', 'Nestled in the Golden city, Jaisalmer Hotel Heera Court is located at a distance of 282 km from Jodhpur Airport while Indira Colony Jaisalmer Railway Station is 3 km and Jaisalmer Border Security Forces Bus Stand is 4.1 km away. Guests can visit majestic and historically significant site such as Vyas Chhatri(550 m), Salim Singh Ki Haveli(1.3 km), Jaisalmer Fort(1.5 km), Gadsisar Lake(2.5 km), Bada Bagh(6.5 km) and many other notable spots during their stay.Heera Court Hotel is a beautiful traditional Haveli style palace in Jaisalmer. For a relaxed and comfortable stay an array of facilities are available such as Wi-Fi access, front desk, laundry, room service and business centre. To keep guests entertain various recreation activities and desert safaris are also arranged. The rooms of the hotel are aesthetically designed, well maintained and fitted with amenities like television, telephone, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. The hotel houses a restaurant which serves a tempting array of scrumptious delicacies to satisfy foodies palate. Furthermore self-service kitchen equipped with dishes, cutlery, stove, pots, glasses, pans and recipes book for our guests that love to cook and who miss their own meal is also available. The on-site bar is the perfect place to invigorate your spirit and incite your soul. Unwind and have a relaxed stay at Hotel Heera Court!', 4471, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
