(3071, 318, 'Shiva Guest House', 'Inside Fort, Kund Para near Laxminath Ji temple', 'Shiva Guest House is located in Jaisalmer, \'Golden city\' of Jaisalmer lies in the far west of the country, encompassing the astounding 12th century Jaisalmer fort. This enticing city of Rajasthan is the most popular tourist spot in the state. One can opt for various means to travel to Jaisalmer, Jaisalmer Airport is the closest airport, the nearest railway station is Jaisalmer Railway Station and there are several buses that connects to various parts of the city. The varying requirements of guests are fulfilled as required conveniences are offered at the hotel. Room and housekeeping service ensures the comfortable stay of the guest long with the cleanliness of the hotel. The clean and ventilated rooms in the hotel are well-maintained and comes with various amenities. The rooms here are perfectly designed and crafted as per the taste of guests to make their stay relaxed and comfortable. Ease out relax and have a lovely stay at the Shiva Guest House!', 7819, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0);
