(3500, 415, 'Summer Plaza Resort-Pure Veg', 'Khinger Road, Near MSEB, Near MSEB', '1.5 km from Bus Depot (Panchgani), 2.2 km from Table Land Lake, Swimming pool, Conference hall, Mini movie theatre, Vegetarian restaurant Nestled in the picturesque hills of Panchgani, Summer Plaza Resort provides easy access to popular tourist spots, including the pristine Table Land Lake. The resort has luxury villas and rooms on offer, most of which features spacious balconies. Air-conditioner, mini fridge and cable TV are fitted in all the rooms. There are luxury bathtubs in the en suite bathrooms. Summer Plaza Resort is the perfect retreat for travellers who want to get away from the chaos and stress of their daily lives. Benefit from Ayurvedic therapies in the spa, de-stress at the well-equipped gym and the large freshwater swimming pool or just sit back and behold the views of the spectacular mountains. For business travellers, the resort has a stylish conference hall where meetings and seminars can be organised. Within the premises, the resort features a mini movie theatre, discotheque, jacuzzi, indoor games facility, outdoor park, skating rink and a beautiful Jain temple. The resort has a stylish vegetarian restaurant that dishes out the best of Continental, South Indian, Gujarati, Pure Jain, Punjabi and Chinese delicacies. Watch latest movies at the on-site mini movie theatre that is equipped with Bose Home Theatre system.', 9454, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
