(3641, 422, 'Jayam Castle', '198 Hollywood Hills Pudhu Nagar,', 'Jayam Castle is an independent bungalow nestled in one of the most famous hill station in India, Ooty. Dotted with lush green lawn and trees all around, the property look beautiful. It is located at the distance of 2.8 km from Ooty Railway Station and Mani Vihar Bus Stand. The nearest airport is Coimbatore airport. Guests can also take taxi services and cabs from Bangalore and Mysore. A well-furnished property is an ideal place for those who want to burst stress from city life. It provides well maintained bed rooms, balcony sit outs, living room and Dinning room. Moreover property also features fully equipped kitchenette. Its easy accessibility to prominent landmarks of the town, simple accommodations and provision of necessary amenities like housekeeping, parking, travel assistance, pick and drop from airport and doctor on call service in case of medical emergencies to ensure a relaxed and comfortable stay. While their stay guests can visit many famous tourist places in and around like Government Museum(1.1 km), Ooty Lake(2.2 km), Kandal Cross Shrine(1.1 km), Government Botanical Garden(3.8 km), Doddabetta Peak(10.2 km) and many others are situated at a feasible distance from the bungalow. Have a delightful experience at the well-menicured lush green surroundings!', 7707, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
