(3643, 422, 'willd wood haven', '8/323 Achakari', 'Wild Wood Haven Resort is located in Achakari village at the foothills of the Nilgiris, which is part of the Western Ghats. The dense forests of Mudhumalai and the Nilgiri hills form a part of the Nilgiri Biosphere and the resort is set right amidst this pristine world of nature, located just 30 kms from Ooty, the Queen of Hills. The property offers front desk, parking, housekeeping and doctor on call service in case of medical emergencies. Wake up to the call of birds. Listen to the gentle whispers of the stream. Take a long walk and watch the mist play with the mountain peaks. The rooms are well maintained comes with basic amenities such as restful beds, clean linen, television, wardrobe, table, chairs and attached bathrooms with hot/cold water and essential toiletries. Guests can spend their time playing indoor/outdoor games or they can even enjoy adventurous activities like trekking, jungle safari, river rafting, camping, visit to tribal villages of Masinagudi and many more on demand. The on site dinning area serves mouth watering regional dishes and coffee on requests. Don\'t forget to sit out in balcony and terrace to watch wild life of Mudumalai forests. Travellers, who want to reach Masinagudi, can take a train for Ooty, from there guests can take taxi to reach the property. Vacationers can take a bus as well from almost all the major cities and towns of Tamilnadu. Nearest airport to the hotel is Coimbatore International Airport. This property is an ideal pick for spending a peaceful vacation, away from the city din!', 4914, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
