(3650, 422, 'The Willow Hill', '58/1, HAVELOCK ROAD, OOTY', 'The Willow Hill is situated in Ooty, a picturesque little town amidst serene lakes, lofty mountains and sprawling grasslands. The hotel offers a delightful and pleasant stay with warmth and hospitality to all the guest. The easy mode of transportation available is Ooty Railway station that is 2.6 km away. The hotel offers an array of modern amenities like front desk, parking, laundry and doctor on call in case of emergency. Also other amenities like laundry, play area and travel assistance is also offered. Guest can take a refreshing dip in the pool. To satisfy a foodies palate, multi-cuisine restaurants are available at the hotel that serve variety of dishes. Well-maintained and spacious rooms available at the property are complete with modern amenities like comfortable beds, television, telephone and attached washroom with hot/cold water supply alongwith essential toiletries. Cool off and have lovely stay at The Willow Hill!', 3857, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3651, 422, 'Orange Pekoe', 'Addavala Bus Stop, Ooty - Kotagiri Road, Kotagiri, Near Ooty, Nilgiri District Mettupalayam - Kotagiri Rd', 'Nestled in a tranquil and lush landscape, away from the maddening city centre, Orange Pekoe features capacious and ergonomic rooms fitted with modern conveniences. In-room amenities include cable television, intercom, WiFi enabled, study table and en suite bathrooms. The hotel is in close proximity to Kodanadu View Point (22.2 km), Jawaharlal Nehru Park (5 km), Catherine Water Falls (12.8 km) and Kotagiri Bus Terminus (4.2 km). Coimbatore Airport is around 82 km away from the hotel. For a relaxed, laid back and convenient stay, Orange Pekoe offers facilities such as health club, room service, WiFi enabled, travel desk and parking space. Services like transfers, shuttle service, guide service and sightseeing options are available at an extra cost. For the convenience of business travellers, this luxurious and well-maintained property houses a well-equipped conference hall and executive lounge, wherein guests can hold meetings and seminars. Spice Inn is a multi-cuisine restaurant that dishes out scrumptious and palatable Chinese, Indian and Thai delicacies and refreshing beverages. Guests can also enjoy panoramic views of tea estate along with delicious meals. At Orange Pekoe, loosen up and dispel the worries and enjoy a relaxed stay amidst lush landscape!', 9922, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3652, 422, 'Hotel Jaysanthi', 'Mysore Road, Opp Ooty Club, Nilgiris, Club Rd', 'Hotel Jaysanthi is located 86.6 km from Coimbatore International Airport, whereas Ooty Railway Station is just 1.3 km and Ooty Bus Station is 1.3 km away. Ooty is situated deep within the Nilagiri hills amidst the nature and hotel is situated in the primal part of Ooty. Some of the prominent tourist excursions in the close vicinity to the hotel are Ooty Lake(2.1 km), Stone House(2.2 km), Kamaraj Sagar Dam(6.6 km), Doddabetta Peak(8.4 km), Nilgiri Mountain Railway Line(22.4 km) and various other tourist attractions. The hotel is ideally located in the center of the town to make every corner of Ooty easily accessible for all types of travelers, be it for pleasure or business. The property augments facilities such as conference hall, business center, doctor on call, laundry, Wi-Fi access, sightseeing, round the clock room service, travel desk, pick up on arrival and drop on departure locally. Beautiful decor and premium furnishings are the highlights of 35 rooms of the hotel which are are tastefully decorated and fitted with contemporary amenities such as daily newspaper, sofa unit, LED television, telephone, intercom, Wi-Fi enabled, heater, hot/cold water, geyser, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. The property features a stylish multi-cuisine restaurant that serves a tempting array of scrumptious delicacies that would surely cajole up the taste-buds to the varied taste of travelers. The decent ornate, pleasant ambiance at Hotel Jayshanti makes you feel all comfortable in no time!', 4721, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
