(3655, 422, 'Glen Park Inn', 'Glen Park Inn, Arni House, Kodappamund Arni Road', 'Enjoying proximity to Ootys famous attractions such as Chocolate Factory (1.4 km) and Stone House Government Museum (1.8 km), Glen Park Inn is popular with leisure travellers. It is around 3 km from Ooty Railway Station.   Facilities such as Wi-Fi, travel assistance, laundry service, parking, currency exchange, safe deposit locker and 24-hour security are offered here.   Book your stay in one of the hotels cottages that are fully furnished and come with a separate living room. Each cottage features LCD TV, refrigerator, wardrobe, work desk, sofa set and hot/cold water supply.   South Indian, Chinese and Continental delights can be relished at the in-house restaurant. Vending machines for beverages are also available. You can avail the in-room service to enjoy meals in the cottage.   Government Botanical Garden (1.4 km) is a must visit for nature lovers. Dont miss out on a chance to see exquisite tea plantations at High Hill Tea Garden (1.6 km).', 9345, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
