(3745, 426, 'Hotel Swaroop', 'Opposite Kitte Bhandari Hall, Bandar Road Ratnagiri', 'Hotel Swaroop is situated in the beautiful city of Ratnagiri. The property is at a distance of 5.5 km from Ratnagiri Airport while Bhoke Railway Station is 20.4 km and Ratnagiri Bus Stand is 1.1 km away. The hotel provides luxury accommodation and facilities, which are a good blend of contemporary design and comfort. Backed by a team of skilled professionals, the property ensures that all needs of guests are fulfilled timely. Every room in the hotel is uniquely designed with cozy interiors and offer exclusive amenities which makes the stay comfortable and joyful for guests. Ease out and have a lovely stay at Hotel Swaroop!', 5642, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3746, 426, 'Hotel Kaanchan', 'MIDC, Mirjole Road, Near Ratnagiri Railway Station', '', 9379, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3747, 426, 'Hotel Sea Rock', '1320, Khareghat Road, Ratnagiri', 'Hotel Sea Rock is located in Ratnagiri. The hotel is an ideal choice for your comfortable and pleasant stay at Konkan region, the paradise. The property is at a 5 km from Ratnagiri Airport while Bhoke Railway Station is 19.7 km and Ratnagiri Bus Stand is 120 m away from the property. Ample conveniences are offered at the hotel to suffice the varying requirements of guests. These include round the clock room service, doctor on call, travel assistance, parking, car rental, transportation and front desk. The rooms in the hotel are well-maintained, ventilated and clean, and come with good quality furniture. Rooms are fitted with amenities like LCD television, telephone, hot/cold water, attached bathroom and various other essential bathroom toiletries. To savor some luscious and enticing Indian delicacies, guests can head to in-house restaurant. Furthermore the on-site bar is an ideal venue to relax and meet friends and business associates in a contemporary and relaxing setting, offering excellent selection of spirits. Have a delightful experience at Hotel Sea Rock!', 5988, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3748, 426, 'Hotel Mangala', 'Near ST stand Ratnagiri', 'Hotel Mangala is located in a port city on the Arabian Sea coast in the southwestern part of Maharashtra, Ratnagiri. It is at a distance of 3 km from Ratnagiri Airport, 18 km from Bhoke Railway Station and 2 km from Ratnagiri Bus Stand. The property has well equipped and comfortable rooms with all the modern amenities to avoid any sort of inconvenience to the guest. Have a pleasant and comfortable stay at Hotel Mangala!', 7747, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3749, 427, 'Anugama Resort', '127, Wandoor Village Wandoor', 'Anugama Resort is a 3 star hotel, located at 19.9 kms from Port Blair Airport and 22.6 kms from Central Bus Stand. Anugama Resort features elegant and well furnished rooms equipped with modern conveniences. In-room amenities include mineral water (chargeable), balcony/sit out and attached bathrooms. The property offers restaurant, garden, dining hall, doctor on call, laundry services, sightseeing, parking facility, airport transfer and taxi services. The hotel houses a multi cuisine restaurant with its chic ambiance, serving its guests with wide array of delicacies that will tickle your taste buds away and sea food lovers do not miss on trying exotic fresh sea food! The hotel is an ultimate location for leisure trip because several tourist destinations are close to hotel like Mahatma Gandhi Marine National Park (1.3 kms), New Wandoor Beach (2.5 kms), Jolly Buoy Island (13.8 kms), Cellular Jail (23.2 kms), Ross Island (24.1 kms) and Chidiya Tapu (30.1 kms). Unwind yourself and have a wonderful stay at Anugama Resort!', 6638, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3750, 427, 'Hotel Sea Shell - Port Blair', 'Marine Hill, Marine Hills', 'Hotel Sea Shell - Port Blair located in Port Blair, lies in close proximity to the Port Blair Airport and offers easy access to the rest of the city. The hotel is a wonderful seaside chalet property that offers visitors to the beautiful Andaman and Nicobar Islands a exquisite location to relax amidst nature.he resort has been built keeping in mind our guests need to unwind, recharge, and rejuvenate in the lap of nature. Offering breath-taking views of the sea, the sunrise and the sunset, the resort is an ideal place to relax and explore an area of outstanding heritage and beauty. The property offers an eclectic mix of fine dining, leisure activities and comprehensive business facilities to its guests. Other facilities include bar, restaurant, outdoor and indoor party hall, conference hall, banquet hall and 24 hour front desk staff. Sea Shell Resort offers luxurious sea-facing rooms that are comfortable and spacious, complete with modern amenities. In-room amenities include: cable television, mineral water, 32 inch LCD TV, mini-bar, electric kettle, superior quality spring mattress, rain shower, and an attached washroom with hot/cold water. While staying here, guests can enjoy Ferry Rides, Scuba Diving, Mangrove Safari and Fishing, and Snorkelling. Cool off and relax at Hotel Sea Shell - Port Blair!', 4332, 4.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(3751, 427, 'Hotel Rhishabh', 'Marine Hill Marine Hills', '', 8329, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3752, 427, 'Tango Waves', 'Near VIP Road, opp chinmaya mission, police lane Portblair', '', 9795, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3753, 427, 'Hotel London', 'No 70-A, M A Rd, Phoenix Bay, Port Blair Portblair', 'Hotel London is situated in the heart of the city portblair. It offers suitable and enjoyable staying service to the guests. It is 3.4 km from Port Blair Airport and 550 m from Central Bus Stand. Various places to visit are Viper Island (1.2 km), Ross Island (3.4 km), Chatham Saw Mill (3.7 km) and Jollybuoy Island (24 km). For comfortable and trouble-free stay, hotel provides ample of facilities. Every room in the hotel is uniquely designed with cozy interiors and offer exclusive facilities and services like air conditioning, television, telephone, room service, sofa and attached bathroom with hot and cold water and necessary toiletries to make the stay relaxed and enjoyable for guests. Have a wonderful stay at Hotel London!', 8547, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3754, 427, 'Hotel Sahara', 'Old Pahargaon, Govt, Polytechnic Road Portblair', 'Hotel Sahara, is located at an accessible distance from Airport, Railway Station and Bus Stand. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks help. The hotel offers facilities like parking, front desk, currency exchange, doctor on call and room service. For accommodation, the property offers spacious, airy and well-lit rooms, featuring simple décor, furnishings and amenities like air conditioning, television, intercom and bathroom with essential bathroom toiletries. Have a nice stay at Hotel Sahara!', 4785, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3755, 427, 'Sahara Reidency', 'Old pahargoan, Govt, Polytechnic road, portblair', 'Sahara Reidency, is located at an accessible distance from Airport, Railway Station and Bus Stand. To explore popular tourist destinations in and around the city, guests can seek tour desks help. The hotel offers facilities like parking, front desk, currency exchange, doctor on call and room service. For accommodation, the property offers spacious, airy and well-lit rooms, featuring simple décor, furnishings and amenities like air conditioning, television, intercom and bathroom with essential bathroom toiletries. Have a nice stay at Sahara Reidency!', 3912, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3756, 427, 'Hotel Vivek', 'Garacharma, portblair', '', 9648, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3757, 427, 'Hotel Anbu International', 'Polytechnic Road, near Govt Polytechnic, Dollygunj Port Blair', 'Hotel Anbu International is located in a town surrounded by attractive lush forest and rugged coastline in Emerald Islands, Port Blair. The nearest airport is the Veer Savarkar International Airport which is well connected to major cities making it convenient for the guest to reach. The property has well equipped rooms with amenities like television, intercom facility and attached bathroom with regular supply of hot and cold water. Room service is available for the convenience of the guest. Hotel facilitates travel desk to make tour arrangements and doctor on call is available for any medical emergency. The hotel has restaurant where guest can enjoy mouthwatering and delicious dishes. Have a memorable and comfortable stay at Hotel Anbu International!', 6821, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3758, 427, 'Da Bay inn', 'Seashore Road, Portblair', 'Da Bay inn is a 1 star property, located at 4.5 km from Port Blair Airport and 2.9 km from Mohanpura Central Bus Stand. Guests can explore interesting places around the property like Samudrika Marine Museum (1.4 km), Anthropological Museum (3.6 km), Andaman Cellular Jail(4.5 km), Water Sports Complex(4.2 km) and Joggers Park(5.1 km). The hotel is known for providing luxury accommodation and facilities, which are a good blend of contemporary design and comfort. To ease the stress of travel the hotel offers an array of facilities such as round the clock room service, front desk and parking. The property houses rooms that are equipped with an encore of impeccable amenities such as television, attached bathroom with hot/cold water and various other essential toiletries. Have a comfortable and stupendous stay at Da Bay inn!', 4171, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(3759, 427, 'The White Coral', 'Bumbanallah, Sippighat Port Blair', 'Nestled among the land of joy and exotic beaches, Port Blair. The White Coral is located within close proximity to the Airport, Railway Station and Bus stand. Popular tourist attractions like Marina Park and Aquarium, Samudrika Marine Museum, Anthropological Museum, Wandoor Beach, Andaman Water Sports Complex and many others are situated within close proximity to the hotel. Amidst the most beautiful landscapes and contemporary interiors, the hotel features various modern facilities suchlike doctor on call, travel desk, power backup, laundry, room service, housekeeping and parking. Moreover, all major debit/credit cards are accepted to provide guests a comfortable and a hassle free stay. Featuring capacious and spotlessly clean rooms equipped with modern conveniences such as cable television, air conditioning, telephone, balcony/sit-out, work desk and attached bathrooms with hot/cold water and essential toiletries. Relish authentic and flavourful vegetarian and non vegetarian dishes in the serene ambience at the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant. Have a fun filled and relaxing stay at The White Coral!', 8698, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(3760, 427, 'Hotel Silver Spring', 'mg road,junglighat port blair', '', 5394, 5.0, 5.0, 4.0),
(3761, 427, 'De Meadows Resorts Pvt Ltd', 'Birdline Junction Post Office calicut', '', 7860, 4.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3762, 427, 'Hotel SKS Goldmine', 'NEAR AIRPORT VIP RD JN,JUNGLIGHAT', 'Situated in the heart of Beautiful historic place of Port Blair. Hotel SKS Goldmine is located at a distance of 1.7 km from Veer Savarkar International Airport and nearest bus stand. Guest can visit famous tourist attraction like Makruzz Private Limited(1.9 km), Samudrika Marine Museum(2.2 km), Andaman Cellular Jail(3.3 km), Ross Island(5.1 km), Corbyns Cove Beach(8.3 km) and many more. A property facilitates food services, front desk to help guest, Wi-Fi, airport pick up service to ensure comfortable stay. The supportive staff of the hotel ensures that all needs of guests are timely fulfilled. Adorned with stylish fittings, all rooms are equipped with air conditioner, bath room amenities, luggage storage, television, housekeeping service, work desk, travel desk, iron/ironing board on request, hot and cold water, hair dryer on request, room service. Ample conveniences are offered at the hotel to suffice the varying requirements of guests. Have a delightful experience at the well-manicured lush green surroundings!', 8725, 5.0, 4.0, 5.0),
(3763, 427, 'Hotel Sentinel', 'Phoenix Bay Phoenix Bay', 'Sentinel is focused towards making your getaway luxurious which offers a complete range of adventure & activities. Contemporary ambience and scrumptious sea food makes your experience grand. Our 52 rooms boutique hotel includes a swimming pool with air-conditioned deluxe, premier, luxury room & super luxury Royal Suites handcrafted with red timber furniture built entirely of padauk wood-found on Andaman Islands. Crystal clear water and sandy beaches in Andamans rated by TIME magazine as the second best beach in Asia gives ideal ambience for honey moon couples and gives family vacation the perfect break. Minutes away from the airport, Sentinel Hotel is a perfect base for those wanting to explore the beautiful town of Port Blair. This 4 star property is close to Cellular Jail, Marina Park Complex, Carbyns Cove Beach and Chatham Saw Mill. Encompassed by green landscapes, this hotel has 53 rooms that are categorised as Deluxe Room, Family Room and Royal Suite. All rooms have private balconies, beautiful furniture and necessary amenities. Business travellers can make use of the conference hall to host meetings. The hall is spacious enough to serve as an ideal venue for parties. Swimming pool, health club and spa are some of the important features of the hotel. The location and the presence of a travel desk, offering exciting tour packages, make the hotel suitable for leisure travellers. To enjoy the best of Indian and international cuisine, head to Coastal Harvest. Sip fine sundowners at Cinque Bar that also serves delicious snacks. Queen\'s Shop that sells beautiful handicrafts and souvenirs is an important highlight of the hotel.', 4774, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3764, 427, 'Hotel Diviyum Manor', 'Opp to Veer Savarkar Airport, Lamba Line,', 'Hotel Diviyum Manor is a budget property offers fuss free and comfortable stay at an affordable range. The hotel provides the best of accommodation and cuisines with highly professional and courteous service. Whether it is a family holiday or a business trip. They cater the best hospitality that makes the stay etched in your memories. The hotel is 4 km from the Port Blair Railway Station and 8 m away from the Veer Savarkar International Airport. Guest can visit nearby excursion like Samudrika Marine Museum (3 km), Andaman Cellular Jail (4 km), Jolly Bouy (21 Km), Chidiya Tapu (22 km), New Wandoor Beach (22 km) and many more. The hotel feature facilities like restaurant, bar, room service, parking facility and many more. The hotel has a total of 15 guest rooms well designed and equipped with air conditioner, intercom facility, mineral water, shower area, geyser in bathroom, hot/cold water, bathroom toiletries. The restaurant at the hotel offers multi-cuisine a-la-carte menu to cater the taste buds of people across the globe. Have a memorable stay at Hotel Diviyum, Manor.', 9220, 5.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3765, 427, 'Andaman Galley', 'central lodge campus,goal ghar,port blair. port blair', 'Hotel Andaman Galley features front desk, parking, large sitting area in reception, housekeeping, security, Wi-Fi, room service, laundry and doctor on call service in case of medical emergencies. Set amidst serene and picturesque surroundings overlooking the Bay of Bengal, the property offers a perfect retreat to spend a relaxing and rejuvenating holiday in Port Blair. The rooms are well maintained and clean. Modern amenities like satellite television, telephone, cozy and restful beds, wardrobe, table, chairs and attached bathrooms with basic toiletries are provided in all the rooms. Guests can enjoy a mesmerizing view of the sea from their rooms. Vacationers can enjoy an array of scrumptious delicacies at the in-house multi cuisine restaurant.    Hotel is located at the distance of 2.3 km from Port Blair Airport and Andaman Cellular Jail,2.6 km from Aberdeen Bazaar Bus Station, for the adventurous and the patience travel, guests can take a passenger ship that heads out to Port Blair from Chennai, Kolkata, and Visakhapatnam. Tickets can be booked at the office of the Shipping Corporation of India. The best part is hotel also provides facility of tour and travel assistance to explore rainforests, Corbyns Cove and exotic marine life of Viper Island, trekking on Mount Harriet and relish numerous water sports like scuba diving, snorkeling, kayaking and more.   Have a memorable stay at Hotel Andaman Galley!', 4260, 4.0, 5.0, 5.0),
(3766, 427, 'Hotel Velocity', 'OppTamizhar Sangam, Phoenix bay Portblair', 'Located in the heart of the city, Hotel Velocity is at a distance of 5.3 km from Veer Savarkar International Airport and 7.6 km from Central Bus Stand. It offers facilities like room service, laundry, power backup and Wi-Fi. The doctor on call facility can be availed during medical emergencies. The property has an advantage as it enjoys propinquity to various tourist places like Jogger\'s Park (5.6 km), Anthropological Museum (7.4 km), Cellular Jail (8.2 km), Samudrika Marine Museum (8.4 km) and Ross Island (9.7 km). The travel desk at the hotel helps guests to organize and plan their tour well. Guests can start their day with a healthy breakfast and enjoy a variety of freshly prepared local and regional delicacies at the in-house multi-cuisine restaurant. Offering finest hospitality, the rooms of the hotel are well maintained and aesthetically designed. The rooms offer amenities like air conditioning, television, tea/coffee maker and telephone. Adorned with stylish fittings, the bathrooms are equipped with essential amenities and bathroom toiletries. Have a nice stay at Hotel Velocity!', 4247, 4.0, 4.0, 4.0),
(3767, 427, 'J Hotel', 'Near Clock Tower Aberdeen Bazaar', '', 4152, 5.0, 4.0, 4.0);
